(72, '145000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}]', 'http://www.themummy.com/', 'en', 'Archaeologist Rick O''Connell travels to China, pitting him against an emperor from the 2,000-year-old Han dynasty who''s returned from the dead to pursue a quest for world domination. This time, O''Connell enlists the help of his wife and son to quash the so-called ''Dragon Emperor'' and his abuse of supernatural power.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "China Film Co-Production Corporation", "id": 2269}, {"name": "Relativity Media", "id": 7295}, {"name": "Alphaville Films", "id": 11462}, {"name": "Sommers Company, The", "id": 19643}]', '2008-07-01', '401128639.00', '112.00', 'A New Evil Awakens.', 'The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor', '5.2', 1387, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTU4NDIzMDY1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjQxMzk3MQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
