(106, '170000000.00', '[{"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}]', 'http://movies.disney.com/alice-through-the-looking-glass', 'en', 'In the sequel to Tim Burton''s "Alice in Wonderland", Alice Kingsleigh returns to Underland and faces a new adventure in saving the Mad Hatter.', '[{"name": "Walt Disney Pictures", "id": 2}, {"name": "Team Todd", "id": 598}, {"name": "Tim Burton Productions", "id": 8601}, {"name": "Roth Films", "id": 16314}, {"name": "Legend3D", "id": 37455}]', '2016-05-25', '299370084.00', '113.00', 'It''s time for a little madness.', 'Alice Through the Looking Glass', '6.5', 1725, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc2NjExMTIyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg0OTIwODE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(107, '160000000.00', '[{"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'http://www.shrekthethird.com/flash/index.html', 'en', 'The King of Far Far Away has died and Shrek and Fiona are to become King &amp; Queen. However, Shrek wants to return to his cozy swamp and live in peace and quiet, so when he finds out there is another heir to the throne, they set off to bring him back to rule the kingdom.', '[{"name": "DreamWorks SKG", "id": 27}, {"name": "DreamWorks Animation", "id": 521}]', '2007-05-17', '798958165.00', '93.00', 'Who''s ready for Thirds?', 'Shrek the Third', '6.0', 2278, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTgyMjc3ODk2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjY0MjEzMw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(108, '160000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}]', 'http://www.warcraft-themovie.com/', 'en', 'The peaceful realm of Azeroth stands on the brink of war as its civilization faces a fearsome race of invaders: orc warriors fleeing their dying home to colonize another. As a portal opens to connect the two worlds, one army faces destruction and the other faces extinction. From opposing sides, two heroes are set on a collision course that will decide the fate of their family, their people, and their home.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "Atlas Entertainment", "id": 507}, {"name": "Legendary Pictures", "id": 923}, {"name": "Blizzard Entertainment", "id": 16028}]', '2016-05-25', '433677183.00', '123.00', 'Two worlds. One home.', 'Warcraft', '6.3', 2268, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjIwNTM0Mzc5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDk5NDU1ODE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,10,190,281_.jpg'),
