(156, '100000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/funwithdickandjane/', 'en', 'After Dick Harper loses his job at Globodyne in an Enron-esque collapse, he and his wife, Jane, turn to crime in order to handle the massive debt they now face. Two intelligent people, Dick and Jane actually get pretty good at robbing people and even enjoy it -- but they have second thoughts when they''re reminded that crime can hurt innocent people. When the couple hears that Globodyne boss Jack McCallister actually swindled the company, they plot revenge.', '[{"name": "Imagine Entertainment", "id": 23}, {"name": "Columbia Pictures Corporation", "id": 441}, {"name": "JC 23 Entertainment", "id": 76714}]', '2005-12-21', '202026112.00', '90.00', 'Giving big businesses a run for their money!', 'Fun with Dick and Jane', '5.9', 627, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTJiMWFiNzgtMDQxZi00NTFiLWE2YjMtNTA5NzY5YzQxZjNjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTIzOTk5ODM@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR5,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(157, '140000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 10752, "name": "War"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Nathan Algren is an American hired to instruct the Japanese army in the ways of modern warfare, which finds him learning to respect the samurai and the honorable principles that rule them. Pressed to destroy the samurai''s way of life in the name of modernization and open trade, Algren decides to become an ultimate warrior himself and to fight for their right to exist.', '[{"name": "Cruise/Wagner Productions", "id": 44}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "Radar Pictures", "id": 14718}, {"name": "Bedford Falls Company, The", "id": 20634}]', '2003-12-05', '456758981.00', '154.00', 'In the face of an enemy, in the heart of one man, lies the soul of a warrior.', 'The Last Samurai', '7.3', 1895, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzkyNzQ1Mzc0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODg3MzUzMw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(158, '140000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}]', 'http://www.exodusgodsandkings.com/', 'en', 'The defiant leader Moses rises up against the Egyptian Pharaoh Ramses, setting 400,000 slaves on a monumental journey of escape from Egypt and its terrifying cycle of deadly plagues.', '[{"name": "Scott Free Productions", "id": 1645}, {"name": "Chernin Entertainment", "id": 7076}, {"name": "Babieka", "id": 20656}, {"name": "Volcano Films", "id": 52184}]', '2014-12-03', '268031828.00', '150.00', 'Once brothers, now enemies.', 'Exodus: Gods and Kings', '5.6', 1921, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjI3MDY0NjkxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTM3NTA0MzE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg');
