(248, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'http://oceans12.warnerbros.com/', 'en', 'Danny Ocean reunites with his old flame and the rest of his merry band of thieves in carrying out three huge heists in Rome, Paris and Amsterdam – but a Europol agent is hot on their heels.', '[{"name": "Village Roadshow Pictures", "id": 79}, {"name": "Section Eight", "id": 129}, {"name": "Jerry Weintraub Productions", "id": 2596}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "WV Films III", "id": 12202}]', '2004-12-09', '362744280.00', '125.00', 'Twelve is the new eleven.', 'Ocean''s Twelve', '6.4', 2124, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMmJmYzBjNTktMTJjZS00ZGRhLWE1Y2QtOWQxZGU0Y2RmMjkyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(249, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'After five (or six) years of vanilla-wedded bliss, ordinary suburbanites John and Jane Smith are stuck in a huge rut. Unbeknownst to each other, they are both coolly lethal, highly-paid assassins working for rival organisations. When they discover they''re each other''s next target, their secret lives collide in a spicy, explosive mix of wicked comedy, pent-up passion, nonstop action and high-tech weaponry.', '[{"name": "Weed Road Pictures", "id": 433}, {"name": "Summit Entertainment", "id": 491}, {"name": "Regency Enterprises", "id": 508}, {"name": "Epsilon Motion Pictures", "id": 1171}, {"name": "New Regency Pictures", "id": 10104}]', '2005-06-07', '478207520.00', '120.00', 'Smart and sexy.', 'Mr. & Mrs. Smith', '6.5', 2965, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTUxMzcxNzQzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzQxNjUyMw@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(250, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'http://www.thedivergentseries.movie/#insurgent', 'en', 'Beatrice Prior must confront her inner demons and continue her fight against a powerful alliance which threatens to tear her society apart.', '[{"name": "Summit Entertainment", "id": 491}, {"name": "Mandeville Films", "id": 10227}, {"name": "Red Wagon Entertainment", "id": 14440}, {"name": "NeoReel", "id": 24097}]', '2015-03-18', '295238201.00', '119.00', 'One Choice Can Destroy You', 'Insurgent', '6.2', 3829, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTgxOTYxMTg3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDgyMzA2NDE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(251, '116000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A biopic depicting the life of filmmaker and aviation pioneer Howard Hughes from 1927 to 1947, during which time he became a successful film producer and an aviation magnate, while simultaneously growing more unstable due to severe obsessive-compulsive disorder.', '[{"name": "Miramax Films", "id": 14}, {"name": "Appian Way", "id": 562}, {"name": "Forward Pass", "id": 675}, {"name": "Cappa Productions", "id": 691}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "Initial Entertainment Group (IEG)", "id": 7380}, {"name": "IMF Internationale Medien und Film GmbH & Co. 3. Produktions KG", "id": 19116}, {"name": "Mel''s Cite du Cinema", "id": 54502}]', '2004-12-17', '102000000.00', '170.00', 'For some men, the sky was the limit. For him, it was just the beginning.', 'The Aviator', '7.0', 1489, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTYzMjA2M2EtYmY1OC00ZWMxLThlY2YtZGI3MTQzOWM4YjE3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(252, '112000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Travel writer Lemuel Gulliver takes an assignment in Bermuda, but ends up on the island of Liliput, where he towers over its tiny citizens.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment", "id": 444}, {"name": "Davis Entertainment", "id": 1302}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment III", "id": 6332}]', '2010-12-25', '237382724.00', '85.00', 'Something big is going down.', 'Gulliver''s Travels', '4.9', 621, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjI1NDU1MjcxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODczNTM1Mw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(253, '120000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/thegreenhornet/', 'en', 'Britt Reid (Seth Rogen), the heir to the largest newspaper fortune in Los Angeles, is a spoiled playboy who has been, thus far, happy to lead an aimless life. After his father (Tom Wilkinson) dies, Britt meets Kato (Jay Chou), a resourceful company employee. Realizing that they have the talent and resources to make something of their lives, Britt and Kato join forces as costumed crime-fighters to bring down the city''s most-powerful criminal, Chudnofsky (Christoph Waltz).', '[{"name": "Original Film", "id": 333}, {"name": "Sony Pictures Entertainment", "id": 5752}, {"name": "Reliance BIG Entertainment", "id": 6733}]', '2011-01-12', '227817248.00', '119.00', 'Breaking the Law to Protect It.', 'The Green Hornet', '5.5', 1251, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTcwOTMwMDYyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzAxMjMyNA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(254, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 10752, "name": "War"}]', 'http://www.300themovie.com/', 'en', 'Based on Frank Miller''s latest graphic novel Xerxes and told in the breathtaking visual style of the blockbuster "300," this new chapter of the epic saga takes the action to a fresh battlefield--on the sea--as Greek general Themistokles attempts to unite all of Greece by leading the charge that will change the course of the war. "300: Rise of an Empire" pits Themistokles against the massive invading Persian forces led by mortal-turned-god Xerxes and Artemesia, the vengeful commander of the Persian navy.', '[{"name": "Legendary Pictures", "id": 923}, {"name": "Hollywood Gang Productions", "id": 2994}, {"name": "Atmosphere Entertainment MM", "id": 2995}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "Nimar Studios", "id": 7636}, {"name": "Cruel and Unusual Films", "id": 78685}]', '2014-03-05', '337580051.00', '102.00', 'Seize your glory!', '300: Rise of an Empire', '6.1', 2397, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTEwNTU2MjAwMDdeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDk2Njc2Njk@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(255, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}]', 'http://www.smurfhappens.com/', 'en', 'When the evil wizard Gargamel chases the tiny blue Smurfs out of their village, they tumble from their magical world and into ours -- in fact, smack dab in the middle of Central Park. Just three apples high and stuck in the Big Apple, the Smurfs must find a way to get back to their village before Gargamel tracks them down.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Sony Pictures Animation", "id": 2251}, {"name": "Kerner Entertainment Company", "id": 7311}]', '2011-07-29', '563749323.00', '103.00', 'Smurf Happens.', 'The Smurfs', '5.5', 1179, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTBiYTBkYTItM2E2OS00NTY2LWE5MmEtZjdjMzkyYTk5MjJiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTA1NjE5MTAz._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(256, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'http://movies.disney.com/home-on-the-range', 'en', 'When a greedy outlaw schemes to take possession of the "Patch Of Heaven" dairy farm, three determined cows, a karate-kicking stallion and a colorful corral of critters join forces to save their home. The stakes are sky-high as this unlikely animal alliance risk their hides and match wits with a mysterious band of bad guys.', '[{"name": "Walt Disney Pictures", "id": 2}]', '2004-04-02', '103951461.00', '76.00', 'Bust a Moo', 'Home on the Range', '5.7', 389, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWIyNWEwZDctMzkzNC00NzkyLTk5YWUtOWQ5MzBhMGE1NTE4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjExODE1MDc@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(257, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}]', 'http://www.thedivergentseries.movie/#allegiant', 'en', 'Beatrice Prior and Tobias Eaton venture into the world outside of the fence and are taken into protective custody by a mysterious agency known as the Bureau of Genetic Welfare.', '[{"name": "Summit Entertainment", "id": 491}, {"name": "Lionsgate", "id": 1632}, {"name": "Mandeville Films", "id": 10227}, {"name": "Red Wagon Entertainment", "id": 14440}]', '2016-03-09', '179246868.00', '121.00', 'Break the boundaries of your world', 'Allegiant', '5.9', 1998, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjk2OTc5YzQtMjAwMS00YWY4LTk1ZWItOTgyMmRkMGU4ZmY1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzQ1MzUwMTE@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR7,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(258, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'http://www.steelgetsreal.com/', 'en', 'In the near-future, Charlie Kenton is a washed-up fighter who retired from the ring when robots took over the sport. After Charlie''s robot is trashed, he reluctantly teams up with his estranged son Max to rebuild and train an unlikely contender.', '[{"name": "DreamWorks SKG", "id": 27}, {"name": "21 Laps Entertainment", "id": 2575}, {"name": "Reliance Entertainment", "id": 7294}, {"name": "Touchstone Pictures", "id": 9195}, {"name": "ImageMovers", "id": 11395}, {"name": "Angry Films", "id": 12087}, {"name": "Revolution Sun Studios", "id": 76043}, {"name": "Kontsept Film Company", "id": 76067}, {"name": "Wardour Street Pictures", "id": 76069}]', '2011-09-28', '299268508.00', '127.00', 'If you get one shot, make it real.', 'Real Steel', '6.6', 2692, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjEzMzEzNjg0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzg4NDk0Ng@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(259, '105000000.00', '[{"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}]', 'http://smurfhappens.com', 'en', 'The evil wizard Gargamel creates a couple of mischievous Smurf-like creatures called the Naughties that he hopes will let him harness the all-powerful, magical Smurf-essence. But when he discovers that only a real Smurf can give him what he wants, and only a secret spell that Smurfette knows can turn the Naughties into real Smurfs, Gargamel kidnaps Smurfette and brings her to Paris, where he has been winning the adoration of millions as the world¹s greatest sorcerer. It''s up to Papa, Clumsy, Grouchy, and Vanity to return to our world, reunite with their human friends Patrick and Grace Winslow, and rescue her! Will Smurfette, who has always felt different from the other Smurfs, find a new connection with the Naughties Vexy and Hackus or will the Smurfs convince her that their love for her is True Blue?', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Sony Pictures Animation", "id": 2251}, {"name": "Kerner Entertainment Company", "id": 7311}, {"name": "Hemisphere Media Capital", "id": 9169}, {"name": "NeoReel", "id": 24097}]', '2013-07-30', '347434178.00', '105.00', 'Get ready to get naughty!', 'The Smurfs 2', '5.5', 695, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMmZmZDc4ODYtYmFkYy00N2UwLThmY2UtNTliZmJiMThiNWU3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTIzOTk5ODM@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(260, '160000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Sandra Bullock and Jason Patric star as a young couple whose dream cruise turns to terror when a lunatic computer genius (Willem Dafoe) sets a new course for destruction.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Blue Tulip Productions", "id": 35304}]', '1997-06-13', '164508066.00', '121.00', 'As the stakes get higher, the ride gets even faster.', 'Speed 2: Cruise Control', '4.1', 434, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2VmMzRhZTQtYjMzYy00ODU2LTk1MWYtYmNmM2IzZWM2M2NmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUyOTc1NDYz._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(261, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}]', 'http://www.if-sentinel.com/', 'en', 'Based on the classic novel by Orson Scott Card, Ender''s Game is the story of the Earth''s most gifted children training to defend their homeplanet in the space wars of the future.', '[{"name": "Summit Entertainment", "id": 491}, {"name": "Chartoff Productions", "id": 3200}, {"name": "Odd Lot Entertainment", "id": 3263}, {"name": "K/O Paper Products", "id": 7296}, {"name": "Digital Domain", "id": 31825}, {"name": "Taleswapper", "id": 31826}]', '2013-10-23', '125537191.00', '114.00', 'This is not a game.', 'Ender''s Game', '6.6', 2303, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjAzMzI5OTgzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTU5MTAwMDE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(262, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'John McClane is back and badder than ever, and this time he''s working for Homeland Security. He calls on the services of a young hacker in his bid to stop a ring of Internet terrorists intent on taking control of America''s computer infrastructure.', '[{"name": "Ingenious Film Partners", "id": 289}, {"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment", "id": 444}, {"name": "Cheyenne Enterprises", "id": 890}, {"name": "Wintergreen Productions", "id": 11845}]', '2007-06-20', '383531464.00', '128.00', 'The old school cop is back!', 'Live Free or Die Hard', '6.4', 2089, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDQxMDE1OTg4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTMzOTQzMw@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(263, '93000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}]', 'http://www.lordoftherings.net/', 'en', 'Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from his uncle Bilbo, must leave his home in order to keep it from falling into the hands of its evil creator. Along the way, a fellowship is formed to protect the ringbearer and make sure that the ring arrives at its final destination: Mt. Doom, the only place where it can be destroyed.', '[{"name": "WingNut Films", "id": 11}, {"name": "New Line Cinema", "id": 12}, {"name": "The Saul Zaentz Company", "id": 5237}]', '2001-12-18', '871368364.00', '178.00', 'One ring to rule them all', 'The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring', '8.0', 8705, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2EyZjM3NzUtNWUzMi00MTgxLWI0NTctMzY4M2VlOTdjZWRiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDUzOTQ5MjY@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(264, '110000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A bet pits a British inventor, a Chinese thief and a French artist on a worldwide adventure that they can circle the globe in 80 days.', '[{"name": "Studio Babelsberg", "id": 264}, {"name": "Walden Media", "id": 10221}, {"name": "Babelsberg Film", "id": 19481}, {"name": "Mostow/Lieberman Productions", "id": 23636}, {"name": "80 Days Productions", "id": 53413}, {"name": "Spanknyce Films", "id": 53414}, {"name": "Fitzwilliam Productions", "id": 53416}]', '2004-06-16', '72178895.00', '120.00', 'Let your imagination soar.', 'Around the World in 80 Days', '5.7', 672, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGI2ODRiYzctMzA4YS00ZThhLWI5NzYtZDRhOGQyNDQyYmE3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc5NjEzNA@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(265, '107000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'In 1964, a brash new pro boxer, fresh from his olympic gold medal victory, explodes on to the scene; Cassius Clay. Bold and outspoken, he cuts an entirely new image for African Americans in sport with his proud public self confidence and his unapologetic belief that he is the greatest boxer of all time. Yet at the top of his game, both Ali''s personal and professional lives face the ultimate test.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures Corporation", "id": 441}]', '2001-12-11', '87713825.00', '157.00', 'Float like a butterfly and sting like a bee.', 'Ali', '6.7', 447, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjA3OTUxNTktN2FlNC00NGUyLWI1NDktY2FlZTc5MDlmOGFhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(266, '0.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Conrad and Sally Walden are home alone with their pet fish. It is raining outside, and there is nothing to do. Until The Cat in the Hat walks in the front door. He introduces them to their imagination, and at first it''s all fun and games, until things get out of hand, and The Cat must go, go, go, before their parents get back.', '[{"name": "Imagine Entertainment", "id": 23}, {"name": "DreamWorks SKG", "id": 27}, {"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}]', '2003-11-21', '0.00', '82.00', 'Don''t mess with the hat.', 'The Cat in the Hat', '4.9', 366, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTI5MDU3MTYyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwODgyODc3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(267, '120000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'In 2035, where robots are common-place and abide by the three laws of robotics, a techno-phobic cop investigates an apparent suicide. Suspecting that a robot may be responsible for the death, his investigation leads him to believe that humanity may be in danger.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Laurence Mark Productions", "id": 415}, {"name": "Davis Entertainment", "id": 1302}, {"name": "Overbrook Entertainment", "id": 12485}, {"name": "Mediastream Vierte Film GmbH & Co. Vermarktungs KG", "id": 19354}, {"name": "Canlaws Productions", "id": 19355}]', '2004-07-15', '347234916.00', '115.00', 'Laws are made to be broken.', 'I, Robot', '6.7', 3793, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmE1OWI2ZGItMDUyOS00MmU5LWE0MzUtYTQ0YzA1YTE5MGYxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDM5ODIyNw@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR9,0,190,281_.jpg'),
