(446, '80000000.00', '[{"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'http://www.justgowithit-movie.com', 'en', 'A plastic surgeon, romancing a much younger schoolteacher, enlists his loyal assistant to pretend to be his soon to be ex-wife, in order to cover up a careless lie. When more lies backfire, the assistant''s kids become involved, and everyone heads off for a weekend in Hawaii that will change all their lives.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Happy Madison Productions", "id": 2608}]', '2011-02-10', '214918407.00', '117.00', 'Sometimes a guy''s best wingman... is a wingwoman', 'Just Go with It', '6.3', 1543, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTM3MzM3NDE5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDE5MTUxNA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
