(448, '80000000.00', '[{"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Jerry Shaw and Rachel Holloman are two strangers whose lives are suddenly thrown into turmoil by a mysterious woman they have never met. Threatening their lives and family, the unseen caller uses everyday technology to control their actions and push them into increasing danger. As events escalate, Jerry and Rachel become the country''s most-wanted fugitives and must figure out what is happening to them.', '[{"name": "DreamWorks SKG", "id": 27}, {"name": "K/O Paper Products", "id": 7296}, {"name": "Goldcrest Pictures", "id": 11843}, {"name": "KMP Film Invest", "id": 20157}]', '2008-09-25', '178066569.00', '118.00', 'Don''t walk. Run.', 'Eagle Eye', '6.3', 1018, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjA5MTMzMDMzNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzUwNDUzMw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(449, '79000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'In this classic story of love and devotion set against the backdrop of the American Civil War, a wounded Confederate soldier named W.P. Inman deserts his unit and travels across the South, aiming to return to his young wife, Ada, who he left behind to tend their farm. As Inman makes his perilous journey home, Ada struggles to keep their home intact with the assistance of Ruby, a mysterious drifter sent to help her by a kindly neighbor.', '[{"name": "Miramax Films", "id": 14}, {"name": "Mirage Enterprises", "id": 932}, {"name": "Castel Film Romania", "id": 1370}, {"name": "Bona Fide Productions", "id": 2570}, {"name": "Cattleya", "id": 10102}]', '2003-12-24', '173013509.00', '154.00', 'Find the strength. Find the courage. No matter what it takes... find the way home.', 'Cold Mountain', '6.7', 533, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY3NTc5NzcyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDM0NjQyMQ@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
