(492, '130000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Set in 79 A.D., POMPEII tells the epic story of Milo, a slave turned invincible gladiator who finds himself in a race against time to save his true love Cassia, the beautiful daughter of a wealthy merchant who has been unwillingly betrothed to a corrupt Roman Senator. As Mount Vesuvius erupts in a torrent of blazing lava, Milo must fight his way out of the arena in order to save his beloved as the once magnificent Pompeii crumbles around him.', '[{"name": "Impact Pictures", "id": 248}, {"name": "TriStar Pictures", "id": 559}, {"name": "Don Carmody Productions", "id": 4253}, {"name": "FilmDistrict", "id": 7263}, {"name": "Constantin Film International", "id": 12162}]', '2014-02-18', '117831631.00', '105.00', 'No warning. No escape.', 'Pompeii', '5.2', 1267, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDE2MTU3NzYwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY4NTk4MDE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
