(551, '73000000.00', '[{"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}]', 'http://www.angrybirds-movie.com/en/', 'en', 'An island populated entirely by happy, flightless birds or almost entirely. In this paradise, Red, a bird with a temper problem, speedy Chuck, and the volatile Bomb have always been outsiders. But when the island is visited by mysterious green piggies, it’s up to these unlikely outcasts to figure out what the pigs are up to.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Rovio Entertainment", "id": 18642}, {"name": "Sony Pictures Imageworks (SPI)", "id": 30692}, {"name": "Rovio Mobile", "id": 50848}, {"name": "Rovio Animation", "id": 91920}]', '2016-05-11', '349779543.00', '97.00', 'Why so angry?', 'The Angry Birds Movie', '5.9', 1022, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY3MjU0NDA0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTc0MTU3OTE@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR4,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(552, '70000000.00', '[{"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}]', 'http://www.warnerbros.com/fools-gold', 'en', 'Treasure hunter Ben "Finn" Finnegan has sunk his marriage to Tess and his trusty boat in his obsessive quest to find the legendary Queen''s Dowry. When he finds a vital clue that may finally pinpoint the treasure''s whereabouts, he drags Tess and her boss, billionaire Nigel Honeycutt, along on the hunt. But Finn is not the only one interested in the gold; his former mentor-turned-enemy Moe Fitch will stop at nothing to beat him to it.', '[{"name": "De Line Pictures", "id": 2609}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}]', '2008-02-07', '111231041.00', '112.00', 'This February True Love Takes a Dive.', 'Fool''s Gold', '5.4', 444, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTU3MTYxMDU5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwNTgwNzc4._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
