(557, '72000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}, {"id": 10752, "name": "War"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Enraged at the slaughter of Murron, his new bride and childhood love, Scottish warrior William Wallace slays a platoon of the local English lord''s soldiers. This leads the village to revolt and, eventually, the entire country to rise up against English rule.', '[{"name": "Icon Entertainment International", "id": 4564}, {"name": "The Ladd Company", "id": 7965}, {"name": "B.H. Finance C.V.", "id": 11353}]', '1995-05-24', '210000000.00', '177.00', 'Every man dies. Not every man truly lives.', 'Braveheart', '7.7', 3336, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzkzMmU0YTYtOWM3My00YzBmLWI0YzctOGYyNTkwMWE5MTJkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
