(824, '53000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'On a US nuclear missile sub, a young first officer stages a mutiny to prevent his trigger happy captain from launching his missiles before confirming his orders to do so.', '[{"name": "Hollywood Pictures", "id": 915}, {"name": "Don Simpson/Jerry Bruckheimer Films", "id": 10288}]', '1995-05-12', '157387195.00', '116.00', 'Danger runs deep.', 'Crimson Tide', '7.0', 498, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMmFkY2IxNTAtMWRiNS00MWU2LWI1NDYtY2YxYTQyYTk5OTBhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDk3NzU2MTQ@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg');
