(825, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/homevideo/thepursuitofhappyness/', 'en', 'The true story of Christopher Gardner, who invests heavily in a device known as a ''Bone Density Scanner'', only to find himself struggle to sell the product as it''s just marginally better than the current technology, and much more expensive. His wife leaves him,  he loses his house, bank account and credit cards and, now forced to live out in the streets with his young son,  he''s desperate to find a steady job. He takes on a job as a stockbroker but, before he can receive pay, he needs to go through 6 months of training, and must sell his devices.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures Corporation", "id": 441}, {"name": "Escape Artists", "id": 1423}, {"name": "Relativity Media", "id": 7295}, {"name": "Overbrook Entertainment", "id": 12485}]', '2006-12-14', '307077295.00', '117.00', 'NA', 'The Pursuit of Happyness', '7.7', 2525, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQ5NjQ0NDI3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDI0MjEzMw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(826, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A claustrophobic, Hitchcockian thriller. A bereaved woman and her daughter are flying home from Berlin to America. At 30,000 feet the child vanishes and nobody admits she was ever on that plane.', '[{"name": "Imagine Entertainment", "id": 23}, {"name": "Touchstone Pictures", "id": 9195}]', '2005-09-22', '223387299.00', '98.00', 'If Someone Took Everything You Live For... How Far Would You Go To Get It Back?', 'Flightplan', '6.1', 772, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNGJkYTNiZjUtOTBhMi00NjY5LTkwZWEtNjBkNmE1YTZlMDc4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(827, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A computer specialist is sued for sexual harassment by a former lover turned boss who initiated the act forcefully, which threatens both his career and his personal life.', '[{"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "Baltimore Pictures", "id": 11407}]', '1994-12-09', '214015089.00', '123.00', 'Sex Is Power.', 'Disclosure', '5.9', 210, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNGQxNTFkNjUtM2EwNi00ZThlLTkzMDItODhkMDIyYzM1Y2MzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjUzOTY1NTc@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(828, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'When guardian angel Seth -- who invisibly watches over the citizens of Los Angeles -- becomes captivated by Maggie, a strong-willed heart surgeon, he ponders trading in his pure, otherworldly existence for a mortal life with his beloved. The couple embarks on a tender but forbidden romance spanning heaven and Earth.', '[{"name": "Atlas Entertainment", "id": 507}, {"name": "Regency Enterprises", "id": 508}, {"name": "Monarchy Enterprises B.V.", "id": 676}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "Taurus Film", "id": 20555}]', '1998-04-10', '198685114.00', '114.00', 'She didn''t believe in angels until she fell in love with one.', 'City of Angels', '6.4', 529, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjk2OTEwNDEtNjVhYi00MzI3LWFhNzctZGUzOWMxMDMwZjJlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(829, '30000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'http://www.miramax.com/movie/kill-bill-volume-1/', 'en', 'An assassin is shot at the altar by her ruthless employer, Bill and other members of their assassination circle – but ''The Bride'' lives to plot her vengeance. Setting out for some payback, she makes a death list and hunts down those who wronged her, saving Bill for last.', '[{"name": "Miramax Films", "id": 14}, {"name": "A Band Apart", "id": 59}, {"name": "Super Cool ManChu", "id": 39121}]', '2003-10-10', '180949000.00', '111.00', 'Go for the kill.', 'Kill Bill: Vol. 1', '7.7', 4949, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzM3NDFhYTAtYmU5Mi00NGRmLTljYjgtMDkyODQ4MjNkMGY2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(830, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'On the verge of bankruptcy and desperate for his big break, aspiring filmmaker Bobby Bowfinger concocts a crazy plan to make his ultimate dream movie. Rallying a ragtag team that includes a starry-eyed ingenue, a has-been diva and a film studio gofer, he sets out to shoot a blockbuster featuring the biggest star in Hollywood, Kit Ramsey -- only without letting Ramsey know he''s in the picture.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}]', '1999-08-12', '0.00', '97.00', 'The con is on.', 'Bowfinger', '6.0', 254, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTJlNzcyMjctOGE5Mi00MzU4LWI1MzUtOGZiYzZlMzYxZmFlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(831, '30000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'The Bride unwaveringly continues on her roaring rampage of revenge against the band of assassins who had tried to kill her and her unborn child. She visits each of her former associates one-by-one, checking off the victims on her Death List Five until there''s nothing left to do … but kill Bill.', '[{"name": "Miramax Films", "id": 14}, {"name": "A Band Apart", "id": 59}, {"name": "Super Cool ManChu", "id": 39121}]', '2004-04-16', '152159461.00', '136.00', 'The bride is back for the final cut.', 'Kill Bill: Vol. 2', '7.6', 3948, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmFiYmJmN2QtNWQwMi00MzliLThiOWMtZjQxNGRhZTQ1MjgyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzQ1ODk3MTQ@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(832, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Ray Tango and Gabriel Cash are narcotics detectives who, while both being extremely successful, can''t stand each other. Crime Lord Yves Perret, furious at the loss of income that Tango and Cash have caused him, frames the two for murder. Caught with the murder weapon on the scene of the crime, the two have no alibi. Thrown into prison with most of the criminals they helped convict, it appears that they are going to have to trust each other if they are to clear their names and catch the evil Perret.', '[{"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}]', '1989-12-22', '63408614.00', '104.00', 'Two of L.A.''s top rival cops are going to have to work together... Even if it kills them.', 'Tango & Cash', '6.1', 458, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTBhYjZjNDktZDE5NC00M2I1LWEzYmEtOGU2ZGRlYjdjMmNlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUzMDUzNTI3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(833, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Madeline is married to Ernest, who was once arch-rival Helen''s fiance. After recovering from a mental breakdown, Helen vows to kill Madeline and steal back Ernest. Unfortunately for everyone, the introduction of a magic potion causes things to be a great deal more complicated than a mere murder plot.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}]', '1992-07-30', '149022650.00', '104.00', 'In one small bottle... The fountain of youth. The secret of eternal life. The power of an ancient potion. Sometimes it works... sometimes it doesn''t.', 'Death Becomes Her', '6.3', 636, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWI1MDUxNzgtZTdjMC00MmFmLTlmYjUtNWM5YzRmNjMwMDY2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUzMDUzNTI3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,3,190,281_.jpg'),
(834, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 37, "name": "Western"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Chon Wang, a clumsy imperial guard trails Princess Pei Pei when she is kidnapped from the Forbidden City and transported to America. Wang follows her captors to Nevada, where he teams up with an unlikely partner, outcast outlaw Roy O''Bannon, and tries to spring the princess from her imprisonment.', '[{"name": "Spyglass Entertainment", "id": 158}, {"name": "Roger Birnbaum Productions", "id": 961}, {"name": "Touchstone Pictures", "id": 9195}]', '2000-05-26', '56932305.00', '110.00', 'The old west meets the far east.', 'Shanghai Noon', '6.2', 735, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTI0MjE2MzUwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwMTk5NjU3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(835, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Terrorists hijack a 747 inbound to Washington D.C., demanding the the release of their imprisoned leader. Intelligence expert David Grant (Kurt Russell) suspects another reason and he is soon the reluctant member of a special assault team that is assigned to intercept the plane and hijackers.', '[{"name": "Silver Pictures", "id": 1885}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}]', '1996-03-15', '121969216.00', '133.00', 'Fasten your seat belts', 'Executive Decision', '5.8', 256, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTFiYzg1ZGUtNTZiOC00MWNmLWFiMmItZGNkOGU2NzE0MTJhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjUzOTY1NTc@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(836, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'http://www.popperspenguins.com/main.html', 'en', 'Jim Carrey stars as Tom Popper, a successful businessman who’s clueless when it comes to the really important things in life...until he inherits six “adorable” penguins, each with its own unique personality. Soon Tom’s rambunctious roommates turn his swank New York apartment into a snowy winter wonderland — and the rest of his world upside-down.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment", "id": 444}, {"name": "Davis Entertainment", "id": 1302}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment III", "id": 6332}]', '2011-06-17', '187361754.00', '94.00', 'NA', 'Mr. Popper''s Penguins', '5.7', 751, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTcwMDI4NjEyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzg5MzEwNQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(837, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}]', 'http://www.forbiddenkingdommovie.com/', 'en', 'An American teenager who is obsessed with Hong Kong cinema and kung-fu classics makes an extraordinary discovery in a Chinatown pawnshop: the legendary stick weapon of the Chinese sage and warrior, the Monkey King. With the lost relic in hand, the teenager unexpectedly finds himself travelling back to ancient China to join a crew of warriors from martial arts lore on a dangerous quest to free the imprisoned Monkey King.', '[{"name": "Casey Silver Productions", "id": 877}, {"name": "China Film Co-Production Corporation", "id": 2269}, {"name": "Huayi Brothers", "id": 3393}, {"name": "Relativity Media", "id": 7295}]', '2008-04-18', '127906624.00', '104.00', 'The battle for eternity is the fantasy of a lifetime.', 'The Forbidden Kingdom', '6.3', 461, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTUwNTExMTg3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDYyMTM2MQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,6,190,281_.jpg'),
(838, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'In this irreverent, hilarious, adventurous buddy comedy for audiences of all ages, directed by Jimmy Hayward (Horton Hears a Who!), two turkeys from opposite sides of the tracks must put aside their differences and team up to travel back in time to change the course of history - and get turkey off the holiday menu for good.', '[{"name": "Reel FX Creative Studios", "id": 2787}, {"name": "Relativity Media", "id": 7295}]', '2013-10-30', '110000000.00', '91.00', 'Hang On To Your Nuggets', 'Free Birds', '5.7', 254, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjE0NjIwMzAwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTIyMzMzMDE@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(839, '50000000.00', '[{"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'After escaping with Newt and Hicks from the alien planet, Ripley crash lands on Fiorina 161, a prison planet and host to a correctional facility. Unfortunately, although Newt and Hicks do not survive the crash, a more unwelcome visitor does. The prison does not allow weapons of any kind, and with aid being a long time away, the prisoners must simply survive in any way they can.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Brandywine Productions", "id": 19747}]', '1992-05-22', '159773545.00', '114.00', 'The bitch is back.', 'Alien³', '6.2', 1633, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTNiYmQzNTctNzAyZC00ODY2LWE3ZjgtODU1NDA0NGI5ZDY1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTMxODk2OTU@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(840, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 36, "name": "History"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10402, "name": "Music"}]', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evita_(film)', 'en', 'The hit musical based on the life of Evita Duarte, a B-movie Argentinian actress who eventually became the wife of Argentinian president and dictator Juan Perón, and the most beloved and hated woman in Argentina.', '[{"name": "Hollywood Pictures", "id": 915}, {"name": "Cinergi Pictures Entertainment", "id": 1504}]', '1996-12-14', '141047179.00', '134.00', 'The Most Anticipated Motion Picture Event of The Year', 'Evita', '5.9', 120, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDNhZGZiMzYtNzkxNy00MGE0LWE4Y2QtOGIwOTM3ZmY5M2QwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzc5MjA3OA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(841, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A briefcase with undisclosed contents – sought by Irish terrorists and the Russian mob – makes its way into criminals'' hands. An Irish liaison assembles a squad of mercenaries, or ''ronin'', and gives them the thorny task of recovering the case.', '[{"name": "United Artists", "id": 60}, {"name": "FGM Entertainment", "id": 2347}]', '1998-09-25', '41610884.00', '122.00', 'Your ally could become your enemy.', 'Ronin', '6.7', 658, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWVkYzliZGEtODIxMi00MDQwLThjMDAtNzI3M2NjYjg4NDE5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjU0OTQ0OTY@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(842, '50000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Sir Robert Beaumont is behind schedule on a railroad in Africa. Enlisting noted engineer John Henry Patterson to right the ship, Beaumont expects results. Everything seems great until the crew discovers the mutilated corpse of the project''s foreman, seemingly killed by a lion. After several more attacks, Patterson calls in famed hunter Charles Remington, who has finally met his match in the bloodthirsty lions.', '[{"name": "Constellation Films", "id": 457}, {"name": "Paramount", "id": 6033}]', '1996-10-11', '75000000.00', '109.00', 'Prey For The Hunters', 'The Ghost and the Darkness', '6.4', 236, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWIwMDIxMDktZTlhYS00YTU3LTg4ZTItNGI4NTU3ZTMzZTViXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUzMDUzNTI3._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(843, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'http://www.paddington.com/', 'en', 'A young Peruvian bear with a passion for all things British travels to London in search of a home. Finding himself lost and alone at Paddington Station, he begins to realize that city life is not all he had imagined - until he meets the kindly Brown family, who read the label around his neck (''Please look after this bear. Thank you.'') and offer him a temporary haven. It looks as though his luck has changed until this rarest of bears catches the eye of a museum taxidermist...', '[{"name": "The Weinstein Company", "id": 308}, {"name": "StudioCanal", "id": 694}, {"name": "TF1 Films Production", "id": 3823}, {"name": "Canal+", "id": 5358}, {"name": "Heyday Films", "id": 7364}, {"name": "Cin\\u00e9+", "id": 10611}, {"name": "Anton Capital Entertainment (ACE)", "id": 20664}, {"name": "TF1", "id": 22123}, {"name": "Amazon Prime Instant Video", "id": 58773}]', '2014-11-27', '259207227.00', '95.00', 'The Adventure Begins', 'Paddington', '7.0', 883, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTAxOTMwOTkwNDZeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDEyMTI1NjMx._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(844, '68000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Four everyday suburban guys come together as an excuse to escape their humdrum lives one night a week. But when they accidentally discover that their town has become overrun with aliens posing as ordinary suburbanites, they have no choice but to save their neighborhood - and the world - from total extermination.', '[{"name": "Ingenious Film Partners", "id": 289}, {"name": "Ingenious Media", "id": 290}, {"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment", "id": 444}, {"name": "21 Laps Entertainment", "id": 2575}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment III", "id": 6332}, {"name": "Big Screen Productions", "id": 10893}, {"name": "Down Productions", "id": 37336}]', '2012-07-26', '68267862.00', '98.00', 'Got Protection?', 'The Watch', '5.3', 881, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjU5MzI1NTk1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzk5NzY5Nw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(845, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'In the wilderness of British Columbia, two hunters are tracked and viciously murdered by Aaron Hallum. Former Special Operations instructor, L.T. Bonham is approached and asked to apprehend Hallum, his former student, who has ''gone rogue'' after suffering severe battle stress from his time in Kosovo.', '[{"name": "Lakeshore Entertainment", "id": 126}, {"name": "Alphaville Films", "id": 11462}]', '2003-03-11', '34234008.00', '94.00', 'Some men should not be found.', 'The Hunted', '6.0', 189, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTM2YmFjNGMtNzU4Yi00NDQ3LWE0OTQtM2U5MzlhMmM5ZGYyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUzMDUzNTI3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(846, '80000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Dr. Ethan Powell, an anthropologist, is in Africa studying apes when he is lost for two years. When he is found, he kills 3 men and puts 2 in the hospital. Cuba Gooding''s character is a psychiatrist who wants to take up the task of trying to get Dr. Powell to speak again and maybe even stand judgment at a trial for his release from prison of mental cases. Along the way, Cuba has to deal with also helping the mental patients that are being abused and neglected. In this process Cuba learns a few things about himself and life, and so does Anthony Hopkins character, Dr. Powell.', '[{"name": "Spyglass Entertainment", "id": 158}, {"name": "Touchstone Pictures", "id": 9195}]', '1999-06-04', '0.00', '126.00', 'NA', 'Instinct', '6.2', 146, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMmM4N2M1ZDgtODM1Mi00YjFiLThjZGQtY2YzMGI1ZjAzYzFjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzExODEzNDA@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR3,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(847, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'In Martha''s Vineyard, Mass., conjoined twins Walt (Greg Kinnear) and Bob Tenor (Matt Damon) make the best of their handicap by being the fastest grill cooks in town. While outgoing Walt hopes to one day become a famous actor, shy Bob prefers to stay out of the spotlight. When a fading Hollywood actress, Cher (Cher), decides to get her show "Honey and the Beaze" cancelled, she hires Walt -- and his brotherly appendage -- as her costars. But their addition surprisingly achieves the opposite.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Conundrum Entertainment", "id": 1156}]', '2003-12-10', '33828318.00', '118.00', 'Whatever happens to the boys, one thing is certain. Nothing will ever come between them.', 'Stuck on You', '5.1', 188, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTYwODE1MTc3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjQxMzQyMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(848, '0.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'http://newline.com/properties/semipro.html', 'en', 'Jackie Moon is the owner, promoter, coach, and star player of the Flint Michigan Tropics of the American Basketball Association (ABA). In 1976 before the ABA collapses, the National Basketball Association (NBA) plans to merge with the best teams of the ABA at the end of the season. Only the top four teams will make the move and the worst teams will fold. The Tropics are the worst team in the league and if they want to make it to the NBA, Jackie Moon must rally his team and start winning. The only problem is the fact that Jackie Moon is not really the coach and star basketball player he thinks he is. To keep his team from oblivion and leave his mark in the city, Jackie Moon must inspire his team to win fourth place in the playoffs.', '[{"name": "New Line Cinema", "id": 12}, {"name": "Donners'' Company", "id": 431}, {"name": "Mosaic Media Group", "id": 748}, {"name": "Road Rebel", "id": 2648}]', '2008-02-28', '33472850.00', '91.00', 'Putting the funk into the dunk.', 'Semi-Pro', '5.4', 251, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc1MjQ4NTc3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTc3NTg1MQ@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(849, '60000000.00', '[{"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'The luxuriantly bearded Pirate Captain is a boundlessly enthusiastic, if somewhat less-than-successful, terror of the High Seas. With a rag-tag crew at his side, and seemingly blind to the impossible odds stacked against him, the Captain has one dream: to beat his bitter rivals Black Bellamy and Cutlass Liz to the much coveted Pirate of the Year Award. It’s a quest that takes our heroes from the shores of exotic Blood Island to the foggy streets of Victorian London. Along the way they battle a diabolical queen and team up with a haplessly smitten young scientist, but never lose sight of what a pirate loves best: adventure!', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Aardman Animations", "id": 297}, {"name": "Sony Pictures Animation", "id": 2251}]', '2012-03-12', '118338361.00', '88.00', 'It''s A Plunderful Life', 'The Pirates! In an Adventure with Scientists!', '6.4', 374, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDhkOGZkZWMtNGI4Mi00ZWI3LTgyYTgtMDU4ZDI3NTNjMWFiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjk1Njg5NTA@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(850, '55000000.00', '[{"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}]', 'http://www.changelingmovie.net', 'en', 'Christine Collins is overjoyed when her kidnapped son is brought back home. But when Christine suspects that the boy returned to her isn''t her child, the police captain has her committed to an asylum.', '[{"name": "Imagine Entertainment", "id": 23}, {"name": "Malpaso Productions", "id": 171}, {"name": "Relativity Media", "id": 7295}]', '2008-01-30', '113020255.00', '141.00', 'To find her son, she did what no one else dared.', 'Changeling', '7.3', 1131, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTA1Mzg3NjIxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzU2NTc5MQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
