(882, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'After Paul D. finds his old slave friend Sethe in Ohio and moves in with her and her daughter Denver, a strange girl comes along by the name of "Beloved". Sethe and Denver take her in and then strange things start to happen...', '[{"name": "Harpo Films", "id": 3298}, {"name": "Touchstone Pictures", "id": 9195}]', '1998-10-16', '0.00', '172.00', 'The past has a life of its own.', 'Beloved', '5.9', 26, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTZlMDFkYjItMjgxYi00MDNhLTg0NDYtNDY1NzJkNDg0MGQ4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzc5MjA3OA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,9,190,281_.jpg'),
(883, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://luckyyoumovie.warnerbros.com/', 'en', 'A professional poker player whose astounding luck at the table fails to translate into his lonesome love life attempts to win the World Series of Poker while simultaneously earning the affections of a beautiful Las Vegas singer.', '[{"name": "Village Roadshow Pictures", "id": 79}, {"name": "Lonely Film Productions GmbH & Co. KG.", "id": 430}, {"name": "Deuce Three Productions", "id": 812}, {"name": "DiNovi Pictures", "id": 813}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}]', '2007-05-01', '5761917.00', '124.00', 'Change your game. Change your life.', 'Lucky You', '5.4', 81, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzcyMzgwNzU2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDcyODYzMw@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(884, '52000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'https://www.facebook.com/CatchMeIfYouCanMovie', 'en', 'A true story about Frank Abagnale Jr. who, before his 19th birthday, successfully conned millions of dollars worth of checks as a Pan Am pilot, doctor, and legal prosecutor. An FBI agent makes it his mission to put him behind bars. But Frank not only eludes capture, he revels in the pursuit.', '[{"name": "Kemp Company", "id": 367}, {"name": "Splendid Pictures", "id": 368}, {"name": "Parkes/MacDonald Productions", "id": 11084}]', '2002-12-25', '352114312.00', '141.00', 'The true story of a real fake.', 'Catch Me If You Can', '7.7', 3795, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY5MzYzNjc5NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwNTUyNTc2._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
