(928, '60000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Luther Krank is fed up with the commerciality of Christmas; he decides to skip the holiday and go on a vacation with his wife instead. But when his daughter decides at the last minute to come home, he must put together a holiday celebration.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "1492 Pictures", "id": 436}, {"name": "Revolution Studios", "id": 497}]', '2004-11-24', '0.00', '99.00', 'No! Ho! Ho!', 'Christmas with the Kranks', '5.2', 193, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQxMDMxODEwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwNzM4OTc2._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
