(1119, '40000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'http://www.themechanicmovie.com/', 'en', 'Arthur Bishop is a ''mechanic'' - an elite assassin with a strict code and unique talent for cleanly eliminating targets. It''s a job that requires professional perfection and total detachment, and Bishop is the best in the business. But when he is ordered to take out his mentor and close friend Harry, Bishop is anything but detached.', '[{"name": "CBS Films", "id": 5490}, {"name": "Millennium Films", "id": 10254}, {"name": "Chartoff-Winkler Productions", "id": 12252}, {"name": "Scared Productions", "id": 22035}, {"name": "Nu Image Entertainment GmbH", "id": 22443}]', '2011-01-13', '51070807.00', '93.00', 'Someone has to fix the problems.', 'The Mechanic', '6.3', 1045, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzJhYjE3NjctMGUzMC00YjVhLTkzYzAtNzhmMWU0ZDBlYzJmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDI3NjU1NzQ@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1120, '42000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'http://www.21jumpstreet-movie.com/', 'en', 'In high school, Schmidt was a dork and Jenko was the popular jock. After graduation, both of them joined the police force and ended up as partners riding bicycles in the city park. Since they are young and look like high school students, they are assigned to an undercover unit to infiltrate a drug ring that is supplying high school students synthetic drugs.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Original Film", "id": 333}, {"name": "Stephen J. Cannell Productions", "id": 5585}, {"name": "Relativity Media", "id": 7295}, {"name": "Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer (MGM)", "id": 8411}]', '2012-03-12', '201585328.00', '109.00', 'They thought the streets were mean. Then they went back to high school.', '21 Jump Street', '6.7', 4074, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTZjNzRjMTMtZDMzNy00Y2ZjLTg0OTAtZjVhNzYyZmJjOTljXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1121, '42000000.00', '[{"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'http://www.notting-hill.com/', 'en', 'The British comedy from director Roger Michell tells the love story between a famous actress and a simple book seller from London. A look into the attempt for famous people to have a personal and private life and the ramifications that follow. Nominated for three Golden Globes in 2000.', '[{"name": "Bookshop Productions", "id": 282}, {"name": "Notting Hill Pictures", "id": 283}, {"name": "Working Title Films", "id": 10163}, {"name": "Polygram Filmed Entertainment", "id": 31080}]', '1999-05-13', '363889678.00', '124.00', 'Can the most famous film star in the world fall for the man on the street?', 'Notting Hill', '7.0', 1262, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTE5OTkwYzYtNDhlNC00MzljLTk1YTktY2IxZjliZmNjMjUzL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(1122, '45000000.00', '[{"id": 16, "name": "Animation"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Having been hopelessly repressed and facing eventual certain death at the British chicken farm where they are held, Rocky the american rooster and Ginger the chicken decide to rebel against the evil Mr. and Mrs. Tweedy, the farm''s owners. Rocky and Ginger lead their fellow chickens in a great escape from the murderous farmers and their farm of doom.', '[{"name": "DreamWorks SKG", "id": 27}, {"name": "Aardman Animations", "id": 297}, {"name": "DreamWorks Animation", "id": 521}, {"name": "Path\\u00e9", "id": 7981}]', '2000-06-21', '224834564.00', '84.00', 'This ain''t no chick flick. It''s poultry in motion.', 'Chicken Run', '6.5', 1150, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDgxNjZlZDYtZGJmZC00Mjg0LWEwYzctYWQ0MWFjNTM3ZmM4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTM5NzI0NDY@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1123, '42000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://www.alongcamepolly.com/', 'en', 'Reuben Feffer is a guy who''s spent his entire life playing it safe. Polly Prince is irresistible as a free-spirit who lives for the thrill of the moment. When these two comically mismatched souls collide, Reuben''s world is turned upside down, as he makes an uproarious attempt to change his life from middle-of-the-road to totally-out-there.', '[{"name": "Jersey Films", "id": 216}, {"name": "Loofah Productions", "id": 53626}]', '2004-01-16', '171963386.00', '90.00', 'For the most cautious man on Earth, life is about to get interesting.', 'Along Came Polly', '5.8', 773, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTcxMDMwODg3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwMTM4NTY3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1124, '40000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Marcus is a successful advertising executive who woos and beds women almost at will. After a company merger he finds that his new boss, the ravishing Jacqueline, is treating him in exactly the same way. Completely traumatised by this, his work goes badly downhill.', '[{"name": "Paramount Pictures", "id": 4}]', '1992-06-30', '70100000.00', '117.00', 'A Player Who''s About to be Played.', 'Boomerang', '5.4', 134, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDZmZDU5MGYtMTU3YS00NDczLWJmOTQtOTdlODk2NmMxZjllXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(1125, '43000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Uptight and straight-laced, FBI Special Agent Sarah Ashburn is a methodical investigator with a reputation for excellence--and hyper-arrogance. Shannon Mullins, one of Boston P.D.''s "finest," is foul-mouthed and has a very short fuse, and uses her gut instinct and street smarts to catch the most elusive criminals. Neither has ever had a partner, or a friend for that matter. When these two wildly incompatible law officers join forces to bring down a ruthless drug lord, they become the last thing anyone expected: Buddies.', '[{"name": "Ingenious Film Partners", "id": 289}, {"name": "Ingenious Media", "id": 290}, {"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Chernin Entertainment", "id": 7076}, {"name": "Big Screen Productions", "id": 10893}, {"name": "TSG Entertainment", "id": 22213}]', '2013-06-27', '158674180.00', '117.00', 'Action''s never been so hot!', 'The Heat', '6.5', 1575, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjA2MDQ2ODM3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDUzMTQ3OQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1126, '31115000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Historical epic. The triumphs and tragedy of the Egyptian queen, Cleopatra.The winner of four Oscars, this epic saga of love, greed and betrayal stars Elizabeth Taylor as the passionate and ambitious Egyptian queen who''s determined to hold on to the throne and seduces the Roman emperor Julius Caesar (Rex Harrison). When Caesar is murdered, she redirects her attentions to his general, Marc Antony (Richard Burton), who vows to take power -- but Caesar''s successor (Roddy McDowall) has other plans.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "MCL Films S.A.", "id": 11451}, {"name": "Walwa Films S.A.", "id": 11452}]', '1963-06-12', '71000000.00', '248.00', 'The motion picture the world has been waiting for!', 'Cleopatra', '6.7', 146, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BY2YyOGFlZWItY2M5OC00NzJhLWJmNDgtZTVjNzIzMDI3YjgyL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc1NTYyMjg@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,4,190,281_.jpg'),
(1127, '0.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A high school biology teacher moonlights as a mixed-martial arts fighter in an effort to raise money to save the school''s music program.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Happy Madison Productions", "id": 2608}, {"name": "Broken Road Productions", "id": 8000}]', '2012-10-11', '73100172.00', '105.00', 'No one will fight for his students like Mr. Voss.', 'Here Comes the Boom', '6.0', 593, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTUxMzEzNDQ0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDI2NTY1OA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1128, '42000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'High powered lawyer Claire Kubik finds her world turned upside down when her husband, who she thought was Tom Kubik, is arrested and is revealed to be Ron Chapman. Chapman is on trial for a murder of Latin American villagers while he was in the Marines. Claire soon learns that to navigate the military justice system, she''ll need help from the somewhat unconventional Charlie Grimes.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Regency Enterprises", "id": 508}, {"name": "Monarch Pictures", "id": 966}, {"name": "Epsilon Motion Pictures", "id": 1171}, {"name": "New Regency Pictures", "id": 10104}, {"name": "Manifest Film Company", "id": 20719}]', '2002-04-03', '63781810.00', '115.00', 'Everything you trust. Everything you know. May be a lie...', 'High Crimes', '6.1', 184, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BY2EwYTAwN2MtYjg4Ni00NjhiLWIyMmYtZWVkMzEwNGM1NWEzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjUzOTY1NTc@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR2,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1129, '42000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Rose Morgan (Barbara Streisand), who still lives with her mother (Lauren Bacall), is a professor of Romantic Literature who desperately longs for passion in her life. Gregory Larkin (Jeff Bridges), a mathematics professor, has been burned by passionate relationships and longs for a sexless union based on friendship and respect.', '[{"name": "TriStar Pictures", "id": 559}, {"name": "Phoenix Pictures", "id": 11317}]', '1996-11-15', '0.00', '126.00', 'A story about just how wrong two people can be before they can be right.', 'The Mirror Has Two Faces', '6.5', 47, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNGQ3ZTEzYzktYTQ5My00MDBkLWFhNjItYjBkMjVmMDZjNGZjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUyNjc3NDQ4._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(1130, '32000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Reporter John Klein is plunged into a world of impossible terror and unthinkable chaos when fate draws him to a sleepy West Virginia town whose residents are being visited by a great winged shape that sows hideous nightmares and fevered visions.', '[{"name": "Lakeshore Entertainment", "id": 126}]', '2002-01-25', '55157539.00', '119.00', 'What do you see?', 'The Mothman Prophecies', '6.1', 305, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjVmNDNjYWYtNzk0Mi00ZTU4LTljNDYtNDczZDE4NGMzZmQwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1131, '42000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Flamboyantly gay Austrian television reporter Bruno stirs up trouble with unsuspecting guests and large crowds through brutally frank interviews and painfully hilarious public displays of homosexuality.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}]', '2009-07-08', '0.00', '83.00', 'Borat was so 2006', 'Brüno', '5.4', 518, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTUwNDIwNDE5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDA2MzA1Mg@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
