(1133, '42000000.00', '[{"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}]', 'http://www.redridinghoodmovie.com/', 'en', 'Valerie is in love with a brooding outsider, Peter, but her parents have arranged for her to marry another man – who is wealthy. Unwilling to lose each other, Valerie and Peter plan to run away together when they learn that Valerie''s older sister has been killed by a werewolf that prowls the dark forest surrounding their village. Hungry for revenge, the people call on famed werewolf hunter, Father Solomon, to help them kill the wolf. But Solomon''s arrival brings unintended consequences as he warns that the wolf, who takes human form by day, could be any one of them.', '[{"name": "Appian Way", "id": 562}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "Random Films", "id": 7262}]', '2011-03-11', '89162162.00', '100.00', 'Who''s afraid?', 'Red Riding Hood', '5.6', 922, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc4NjYyMzQ5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjE5Mjc3NA@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1134, '60000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'When Eastern European criminals Oleg and Emil come to New York City to pick up their share of a heist score, Oleg steals a video camera and starts filming their activities, both legal and illegal. When they learn how the American media circus can make a remorseless killer look like the victim and make them rich, they target media-savvy NYPD Homicide Detective Eddie Flemming and media-naive FDNY Fire Marshal Jordy Warsaw, the cops investigating their murder and torching of their former criminal partner, filming everything to sell to the local tabloid TV show "Top Story."', '[{"name": "New Line Cinema", "id": 12}, {"name": "Industry Entertainment", "id": 376}, {"name": "Tribeca Productions", "id": 11391}, {"name": "New Redemption Pictures", "id": 67171}]', '2001-03-01', '56359980.00', '120.00', 'America Likes to Watch', '15 Minutes', '5.7', 191, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWFkZDE5Y2EtYjQ2Ni00OWY2LTgyOGMtN2I5NzEzYWZiNmVlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjk1Njg5NTA@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR3,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1135, '48000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Mario and Luigi, plumbers from Brooklyn, find themselves in an alternate universe where evolved dinosaurs live in hi-tech squalor. They''re the only hope to save our universe from invasion by the dino dictator, Koopa.', '[{"name": "Hollywood Pictures", "id": 915}, {"name": "Cinergi Pictures Entertainment", "id": 1504}, {"name": "Allied Filmmakers", "id": 1755}, {"name": "Walt Disney", "id": 5888}, {"name": "Nintendo", "id": 12288}]', '1993-05-28', '20915465.00', '104.00', 'This Ain''t No Game.', 'Super Mario Bros.', '4.0', 232, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGVmZTUyZDAtYjg0MC00NmE5LWE2OTAtM2FjNGI1NWUyMzE0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjMwMjk0MTQ@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
