(1407, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Mary and Joseph make the hard journey to Bethlehem for a blessed event in this retelling of the Nativity story. This meticulously researched and visually lush adaptation of the biblical tale follows the pair on their arduous path to their arrival in a small village, where they find shelter in a quiet manger and Jesus is born.', '[{"name": "New Line Cinema", "id": 12}, {"name": "Sound for Film", "id": 1143}, {"name": "Temple Hill Entertainment", "id": 12292}]', '2006-12-01', '0.00', '101.00', 'Her child would change the world.', 'The Nativity Story', '6.4', 35, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc0MDM4MzM4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTczNzUzMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1408, '40000000.00', '[{"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A group of unwitting teens are stranded near a strange wax museum and soon must fight to survive and keep from becoming the next exhibit.', '[{"name": "Village Roadshow Pictures", "id": 79}, {"name": "Dark Castle Entertainment", "id": 1786}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}]', '2005-04-30', '68766121.00', '113.00', 'Prey. Slay. Display', 'House of Wax', '5.5', 677, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDA4Nzg1NjQ2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDYwNTgyMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1409, '27000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A witty, romantic, and very dangerous love story about chance meetings, instant attractions, and casual betrayals. Two couples disintegrate when they begin destructive adulterous affairs with each other.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}]', '2004-12-01', '115505027.00', '104.00', 'If you believe in love at first sight, you never stop looking.', 'Closer', '6.7', 811, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2I0Y2JmZjQtNjEyOC00ODhkLWE5YWUtOWFkOGQwMGYyODRiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDk3NzU2MTQ@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1410, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}]', 'http://jedgarmovie.warnerbros.com/dvd/', 'en', 'As the face of law enforcement in America for almost 50 years, J. Edgar Hoover was feared and admired, reviled and revered. But behind closed doors, he held secrets that would have destroyed his image, his career and his life.', '[{"name": "Imagine Entertainment", "id": 23}, {"name": "Malpaso Productions", "id": 171}, {"name": "Wintergreen Productions", "id": 11845}]', '2011-11-09', '84606030.00', '137.00', 'The most powerful man in the world.', 'J. Edgar', '6.0', 741, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc0NDM4ODU2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzQ0NTg4Ng@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,6,190,281_.jpg'),
(1411, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'An ex-cop and his family are the target of an evil force that is using mirrors as a gateway into their home.', '[{"name": "Regency Enterprises", "id": 508}, {"name": "Castel Film Romania", "id": 1370}, {"name": "ASAF", "id": 3273}, {"name": "New Regency Pictures", "id": 10104}, {"name": "Luna Pictures", "id": 15361}]', '2008-08-15', '72436439.00', '110.00', 'There is evil...On the other side.', 'Mirrors', '6.0', 485, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTI2NTA1ODEyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjc3MjY3MQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1412, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Lestat de Lioncourt is awakened from his slumber. Bored with his existence he has now become this generations new Rock God. While in the course of time, another has arisen, Akasha, the Queen of the Vampires and the Dammed. He want''s immortal fame, his fellow vampires want him eternally dead for his betrayal, and the Queen want''s him for her King. Who will be the first to reach him? Who shall win?', '[{"name": "Village Roadshow Pictures", "id": 79}, {"name": "NPV Entertainment", "id": 172}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "WV Films LLC", "id": 67988}, {"name": "Material", "id": 67989}]', '2002-02-10', '45479110.00', '101.00', 'This time there are no interviews.', 'Queen of the Damned', '5.4', 239, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTYxNDEyMzEzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwMDM1NjA3._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1413, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Ten years after a band of mercenaries first battled a vicious alien, the invisible creature from another world has returned to Earth -- and this time, it''s drawn to the gang-ruled and ravaged city of Los Angeles. When it starts murdering drug dealers, detective-lieutenant Mike Harrigan and his police force set out to capture the creature, ignoring warnings from a mysterious government agent to stay away.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Lawrence Gordon Productions", "id": 840}, {"name": "Davis Entertainment", "id": 1302}, {"name": "Silver Pictures", "id": 1885}]', '1990-11-20', '57120318.00', '108.00', 'Silent. Invisible. Invincible. He''s in town with a few days to kill.', 'Predator 2', '5.9', 730, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZmVlNGZjNTktMTQ0Yi00MjkxLWFkYjQtMmJiOTZhNmNiNWJlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTcwOTQzOTYy._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1414, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/untraceable/', 'en', 'Special Agent Jennifer Marsh (Diane Lane) works in an elite division of the FBI dedicated to fighting cybercrime. She thinks she has seen it all, until a particularly sadistic criminal arises on the Internet. This tech-savvy killer posts live feeds of his crimes on his website; the more hits the site gets, the faster the victim dies. Marsh and her team must find the elusive killer before time runs out.', '[{"name": "Lakeshore Entertainment", "id": 126}, {"name": "Cohen/Pearl Productions", "id": 2397}, {"name": "Screen Gems", "id": 3287}]', '2008-01-22', '32483410.00', '101.00', 'A cyber killer has finally found the perfect accomplice: You.', 'Untraceable', '5.9', 238, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTYyNTcwODYzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjMwMzU1MQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1415, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Following a bomb scare in the 1960s that locked the Webers into their bomb shelter for 35 years, Adam now ventures forth into Los Angeles to obtain food and supplies for his family, and a non-mutant wife for himself.', '[{"name": "New Line Cinema", "id": 12}, {"name": "Forge", "id": 2980}, {"name": "Midnight Sun Pictures", "id": 17887}]', '1999-02-12', '40263020.00', '112.00', 'She''d never met anyone like him. He''s never met anyone... Period.', 'Blast from the Past', '6.3', 245, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGFiZjRhMTYtZmMzYS00MGEyLWEzN2EtNWMzMjA3OGI0NGZlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTAyODkwOQ@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR11,0,190,281_.jpg');
