(1417, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Ollie Trinke is a young, suave music publicist who seems to have it all, with a new wife and a baby on the way. But life deals him a bum hand when he''s suddenly faced with single fatherhood, a defunct career and having to move in with his father. To bounce back, it takes a new love and the courage instilled in him by his daughter.', '[{"name": "Miramax Films", "id": 14}, {"name": "Beverly Detroit", "id": 267}, {"name": "View Askew Productions", "id": 16934}, {"name": "Close Call Films", "id": 23022}]', '2004-03-25', '36098382.00', '102.00', 'He wanted it all...but he got more than he bargained for.', 'Jersey Girl', '5.8', 325, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTYxMTZlNTEtMjlmZS00ODFiLTg5ODUtYzJkMzc1MGNhYjVkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
