(1452, '35000000.00', '[{"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Jack Shepard is an out-of-shape auto shop owner, far removed from the man who once protected the world''s freedom. Reluctantly called back into action by the government, Jack is tasked with turning a rag tag group of kids with special powers into a new generation of superheroes to save the world from certain destruction. Based on Jason Lethcoe''s graphic novel "Zoom''s Academy for the Super Gifted".', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Revolution Studios", "id": 497}]', '2006-08-11', '12506188.00', '83.00', 'They''re going to save the world... as long as they''re home for dinner.', 'Zoom', '4.9', 135, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTM0NjczMzUyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDEwMjQzMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
