(1462, '38000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10752, "name": "War"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 37, "name": "Western"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Ride with the Devil follows four people who are fighting for truth and justice amidst the turmoil of the American Civil War. Director Ang Lee takes us to a no man''s land on the Missouri/Kansas border where a staunch loyalist, an immigrant''s son, a freed slave, and a young widow form an unlikely friendship as they learn how to survive in an uncertain time. In a place without rules and redefine the meaning of bravery and honor.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "Good Machine", "id": 10565}]', '1999-11-24', '635096.00', '138.00', 'In a No-man''s Land between North and South, You didn''t fight for the Blue or the Grey... You fought for your friends and family.', 'Ride with the Devil', '6.6', 49, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTRhYTQ2MTAtYzNlYS00MTU1LWEzZmEtZWYxZTM3ZTkxZmM3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTY5Nzc4MDY@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1463, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'es', 'This is a story of a man in free fall. On the road to redemption, darkness lights his way. Connected with the afterlife, Uxbal is a tragic hero and father of two who''s sensing the danger of death. He struggles with a tainted reality and a fate that works against him in order to forgive, for love, and forever.', '[{"name": "Ikiru Films", "id": 2875}, {"name": "Mod Producciones", "id": 5444}, {"name": "Televisi\\u00f3n Espa\\u00f1ola (TVE)", "id": 6639}, {"name": "Menageatroz", "id": 7116}, {"name": "Televisi\\u00f3 de Catalunya (TV3)", "id": 8530}, {"name": "Focus Features", "id": 10146}]', '2010-10-20', '25147786.00', '148.00', 'You don''t choose your family. We all belong to somebody, but to belong to Uxbal and Marambra, is both a blessing and a curse.', 'Biutiful', '7.0', 291, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzI4OTQ0MDQyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODY5MjQwNA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
