(1465, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'In this action thriller set in post-Katrina New Orleans, business owner Jack Vermillion (Laurence Fishburne) is struggling to run a legitimate shipping company while bad guy Ernest Pike (Karl Urban) is struggling to get his family''s illegal gun collection out of the country. When their paths collide, Jack realizes that exposing Pike might get him just the sway he needs to persuade law enforcement officials to treat his imprisoned son kindly.', '[{"name": "Capitol Films", "id": 826}]', '2009-05-13', '0.00', '100.00', 'NA', 'Black Water Transit', '0.0', 0, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWFhZWEwYjktYzQzMi00ZTlhLTg2NzUtOTJiNDRkZTdmOTZjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMjk0NjI@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR13,0,190,281_.jpg'),
