(1783, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Hard-edged cop John Kimble gets more than he bargained for when he goes undercover as a kindergarten teacher to get the goods on a brutal drug lord while at the same time protecting the man''s young son. Pitted against a class of boisterous moppets whose antics try his patience and test his mettle, Kimble may have met his match … in more ways than one.', '[{"name": "Imagine Entertainment", "id": 23}, {"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}]', '1990-12-21', '201957688.00', '111.00', 'Go ahead, you tell him you didn''t do your homework.', 'Kindergarten Cop', '5.8', 628, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjMyMTIyOTc0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY1NTk4NjE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(1784, '27000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/pineappleexpress/', 'en', 'A stoner and his dealer are forced to go on the run from the police after the pothead witnesses a cop commit a murder.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures", "id": 5}, {"name": "Apatow Productions", "id": 10105}]', '2008-08-06', '101624843.00', '111.00', 'Put this in your pipe and smoke it.', 'Pineapple Express', '6.6', 1148, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY1MTE4NzAwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzg3Mjg2MQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(1785, '26000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A unique 16th century woman, Danielle possesses a love of books, and can easily quote from Sir Thomas More’s Utopia. An intriguing mix of tomboyish athleticism and physical beauty, she has more than enough charm to capture the heart of a prince ... after beaning him with an apple.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}]', '1998-07-31', '65705772.00', '121.00', 'Desire. Defy. Escape.', 'Ever After: A Cinderella Story', '6.8', 399, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2FhYTY5ODItOGU4OC00MTkyLTlmYTMtYjIxN2Y4MmVlMDVhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
