(1903, '30000000.00', '[{"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}]', 'http://thebox-movie.warnerbros.com/', 'en', 'Norma and Arthur Lewis, a suburban couple with a young child, receive a simple wooden box as a gift, which bears fatal and irrevocable consequences. A mysterious stranger delivers the message that the box promises to bestow upon its owner $1 million with the press of a button. However pressing this button will simultaneously cause the death of another human being somewhere in the world; someone they don''t know. With just 24 hours to have the box in their possession, Norma and Arthur find themselves in the cross-hairs of a startling moral dilemma and must face the true nature of their humanity.', '[{"name": "Media Rights Capital", "id": 2531}, {"name": "Lin Pictures", "id": 2723}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "Darko Entertainment", "id": 12622}, {"name": "Radar Pictures", "id": 14718}]', '2009-09-17', '33333531.00', '115.00', 'All you have to do is push the button.', 'The Box', '5.4', 597, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTI4MDA5NjIwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTA2MjY0Mg@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
