(1958, '14000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Dangerous Liaisons is the film based on the novel of the same name by Choderlos de Laclos set in 18th century France. Marquise de Merteuil’s asks her ex-lover Vicomte de Valmont to seduce the future wife of another ex-lover of hers in return for one last night with her. Yet things don’t go as planned in this love triangle drama.', '[{"name": "Lorimar Film Entertainment", "id": 1176}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "NFH Productions", "id": 18737}]', '1988-12-16', '34670720.00', '119.00', 'Lust. Seduction. Revenge. The Game As You''ve Never Seen It Played Before.', 'Dangerous Liaisons', '7.0', 257, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzA4MTNjYmQtNTc3Mi00MGNkLWE4M2MtMTgyZjg2ZmY5MGRlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUzMDUzNTI3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
