(2061, '22000000.00', '[{"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Two brothers live in the economically-depressed Rust Belt, when a cruel twist of fate lands one in prison. His brother is then lured into one of the most violent crime rings in the Northeast.', '[{"name": "Appian Way", "id": 562}, {"name": "Scott Free Productions", "id": 1645}, {"name": "Relativity Media", "id": 7295}, {"name": "Energy Entertainment", "id": 18617}, {"name": "Red Granite Pictures", "id": 19177}]', '2013-12-06', '15400000.00', '116.00', 'Sometimes your battles choose you.', 'Out of the Furnace', '6.5', 720, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTEzOWJiZjktZTA1Yy00NDIzLWFiY2UtZGU1M2FmZDVjN2Y3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTY5Nzc4MDY@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
