(2074, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'http://www.forcoloredgirlsmovie.com/', 'en', 'About existence from the perspective of 20 nameless black females. Each of the women portray one of the characters represented in the collection of twenty poems, revealing different issues that impact women in general and women of color in particular.', '[{"name": "Lions Gate Films", "id": 35}]', '2010-11-05', '37000000.00', '134.00', 'Many voices. One poem.', 'For Colored Girls', '7.0', 22, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTExMTA5NjkxNjVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDg0NDM5OTM@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2075, '21000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Former Special Forces officer, Frank Martin will deliver anything to anyone for the right price, and his no-questions-asked policy puts him in high demand. But when he realizes his latest cargo is alive, it sets in motion a dangerous chain of events. The bound and gagged Lai is being smuggled to France by a shady American businessman, and Frank works to save her as his own illegal activities are uncovered by a French detective.', '[{"name": "TF1 Films Productions", "id": 356}, {"name": "Current Entertainment", "id": 972}, {"name": "Canal+", "id": 5358}, {"name": "EuropaCorp", "id": 6896}]', '2002-10-02', '43928932.00', '92.00', 'Rules are made to be broken.', 'The Transporter', '6.6', 1692, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTk2NDc2MDAxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwNDc1NDY2._V1_QL75_UY281_CR3,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2076, '20000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}]', 'http://www.neverbackdownthemovie.com/', 'en', 'Rebellious Jake Tyler is lured into an ultimate underground fight Scene at his new high school, after receiving threats to the safety of his friends and family Jake decides to seek the mentoring of a veteran fighter who trains him for one final no-holds-barred elimination fight with his nemesis and local martial arts champion Ryan McCarthy.', '[{"name": "Summit Entertainment", "id": 491}, {"name": "Mandalay Pictures", "id": 551}, {"name": "Baumgarten Management and Productions (BMP)", "id": 23423}]', '2008-03-04', '41627431.00', '115.00', 'Win or lose... Everyone has their fight.', 'Never Back Down', '6.4', 497, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTkzNDg3MTIyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTAwNDc1MQ@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2077, '21000000.00', '[{"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'After the suicide of her only friend, Rachel has never felt more on the outside. The one person who reached out to her, Jessie, also happens to be part of the popular crowd that lives to torment outsiders like her. But Rachel has something else that separates her from the rest, a secret amazing ability to move things with her mind. Sue Snell, the only survivor of Carrie White''s rampage twenty-two years ago, may hold the key to helping Rachel come to terms with her awesome, but unwanted power. But as Rachel slowly learns to trust, a terrible trap is being laid for her. And making her angry could prove to be fatal.', '[{"name": "United Artists", "id": 60}, {"name": "Red Bank Films", "id": 2229}]', '1999-03-11', '17762705.00', '104.00', 'Looks Can Kill', 'The Rage: Carrie 2', '5.1', 76, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDZmMzE0NjUtZTIzNC00Mzc0LTgyZjgtNzUxMWRiMDIzMDQwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc5NjEzNA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(2078, '17000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Verona and Burt have moved to Colorado to be close to Burt''s parents but, with Veronica expecting their first child, Burt’s parents decide to move to Belgium, now leaving them in a place they hate and without a support structure in place. They set off on a whirlwind tour of of disparate locations where they have friends or relatives, sampling not only different cities and climates but also different families. Along the way they realize that the journey is less about discovering where they want to live and more about figuring out what type of parents they want to be.', '[{"name": "Neal Street Productions", "id": 1522}, {"name": "Focus Features", "id": 10146}, {"name": "Big Beach Films", "id": 12808}]', '2009-06-05', '14899417.00', '98.00', 'NA', 'Away We Go', '6.7', 189, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTYxNzE3NjAwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODkxOTI0Mg@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,6,190,281_.jpg'),
