(2125, '20000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A young interracial couple has just moved into their California dream home when they become the target of their next-door neighbor, who disapproves of their relationship. A tightly wound LAPD officer has appointed himself the watchdog of the neighborhood. His nightly foot patrols and overly watchful eyes bring comfort to some, but he becomes increasingly aggressive to the newlyweds. These persistent intrusions into their lives cause the couple to fight back.', '[{"name": "Screen Gems", "id": 3287}, {"name": "Overbrook Entertainment", "id": 12485}]', '2008-09-19', '27640028.00', '110.00', 'What Could Be Safer Than Living Next to a Cop?', 'Lakeview Terrace', '5.9', 292, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTI0MzI0NDI4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTk4ODk3MQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2126, '20000000.00', '[{"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/homevideo/thegrudge2/', 'en', 'In Tokyo, a young woman is exposed to the same mysterious curse that afflicted her sister. The supernatural force, which fills a person with rage before spreading to its next victim, brings together a group of previously unrelated people who attempt to unlock its secret to save their lives.', '[{"name": "Columbia Pictures Corporation", "id": 441}, {"name": "Ghost House Pictures", "id": 768}, {"name": "Vertigo Entertainment", "id": 829}]', '2006-10-13', '39143839.00', '102.00', 'What Was Once Trapped, Will Now Be Unleashed', 'The Grudge 2', '5.2', 283, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjE3NDIxMDc2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTg2MTkzMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2127, '20000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Through good times and bad, Stella and Delilah have always had each other. Now, Stella''s so busy building a life that she''s forgotten how to really live. But Delilah is about to change all that. What starts as a quick trip to Jamaica, end as an exhilarating voyage of self discovery as Stella learns to open her heart and find love - even if it''s with a man 20 years her junior.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}]', '1998-08-14', '37672350.00', '124.00', 'Sometimes you have to break the rules to free your heart.', 'How Stella Got Her Groove Back', '6.0', 24, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjhlNzMxZDEtYmFjNy00ZjM5LWE1YmQtOTM1YTFmMTIxZGZiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTMxMTY0OTQ@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(2128, '0.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Amiable slackers Bill and Ted are once again roped into a fantastical adventure when De Nomolos, a villain from the future, sends evil robot duplicates of the two lads to terminate and replace them. The robot doubles actually succeed in killing Bill and Ted, but the two are determined to escape the afterlife, challenging the Grim Reaper to a series of games in order to return to the land of the living.', '[{"name": "Orion Pictures", "id": 41}, {"name": "Nelson Entertainment", "id": 365}]', '1991-07-19', '0.00', '98.00', 'Once... they made history. Now... they are history.', 'Bill & Ted''s Bogus Journey', '5.9', 308, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjdlNTZhODktZGU4NS00N2JkLWJjZGMtNWNkNzA3YjkzYjRmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUzMDUzNTI3._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,4,190,281_.jpg'),
(2129, '20000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'The irreverent host of a political satire talk show decides to run for president and expose corruption in Washington. His stunt goes further than he expects when he actually wins the election, but a software engineer suspects that a computer glitch is responsible for his surprising victory.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "Morgan Creek Productions", "id": 10210}]', '2006-10-09', '41237648.00', '115.00', 'Elections are made to be broken.', 'Man of the Year', '5.8', 129, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTM0NzQxMjk0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDUyNDgzMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg');
