(2356, '18000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://www.iloveyoubethcoopermovie.com/', 'en', 'Nerdy teenager Denis Cooverman (Paul Rust) harbors a secret crush on Beth Cooper (Hayden Panettiere), the hottest girl in high school. During his graduation speech, Denis lets the cat out of the bag and declares his love for Beth, who, instead of dissing Denis, shows up at his house later that day and promises to show him the time of his life.', '[{"name": "Ingenious Film Partners", "id": 289}, {"name": "1492 Pictures", "id": 436}, {"name": "Fox Atomic", "id": 2890}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment III", "id": 6332}, {"name": "Bece Canada Productions", "id": 11755}]', '2009-07-10', '0.00', '102.00', 'Popularity is nice. Popular girls are not.', 'I Love You, Beth Cooper', '5.1', 197, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTgyNTc2NDM3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjU3Mzg0Mg@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2357, '18000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://youthinrevolt-themovie.com/', 'en', 'Nick Twisp (Michael Cera), a teen with a taste for the finer things in life like Sinatra and Fellini, falls hopelessly in love with the beautiful, free-spirited Sheeni Saunders (Portia Doubleday) while on a family vacation.  But family, geography and jealous ex-lovers conspire to keep these two apart. Nick abandons his dull, predictable life and develops a rebellious alter ego: François.  With his ascot, his moustache and his cigarette, François will stop at nothing to be with Sheeni, and leads Nick on a path of destruction with unpredictable consequences..', '[{"name": "Dimension Films", "id": 7405}]', '2009-09-11', '0.00', '87.00', 'Every "Revolution" Needs A Leader', 'Youth in Revolt', '5.9', 319, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjE3NTkxODUwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjE4NjI5Mg@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
