(2415, '17000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Matt Sullivan''s last big relationship ended in disaster and ever since his heart''s been aching and his commitment''s been lacking. Then came Lent, that time of year when everybody gives something up. That''s when Matt decides to go where no man''s gone before and make a vow: No sex. Whatsoever. For 40 straight days. At first he has everything under control. That is until the woman of his dreams, Erica, walks into his life.', '[{"name": "Miramax Films", "id": 14}, {"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "Working Title Films", "id": 10163}]', '2002-03-01', '0.00', '94.00', 'Easier said than done.', '40 Days and 40 Nights', '5.2', 297, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjY1ZWYwM2MtNDk0YS00NjY5LWJiYzQtZjVmYmNlN2Y0MzVkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDk3NzU2MTQ@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2416, '17000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Despite being well into adulthood, brothers Doug and Steve Butabi still live at home and work in the flower shop owned by their dad. They exist only to hit on women at discos, though they''re routinely unsuccessful until a chance run-in with Richard Grieco gets them inside the swank Roxbury club. Mistaken for high rollers, they meet their dream women, Vivica and Cambi, and resolve to open a club of their own.', '[{"name": "Paramount Pictures", "id": 4}, {"name": "SNL Studios", "id": 2822}]', '1998-10-01', '30331165.00', '81.00', 'Score!', 'A Night at the Roxbury', '5.9', 198, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTFjYmQ2ZTAtNGE4YS00NzMxLWIwZjItMjcyYzdjODRmZWQ1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTY5Nzc4MDY@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR3,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2417, '17000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://www.beastlythemovie.com/', 'en', 'A curse transforms a handsome and arrogant young man into everything he detests in this contemporary retelling of Beauty and the Beast. Wealthy Kyle Kingson has everything a teenager could want in life, but he still gets off on humiliating the weaker and less attractive. When Kyle invites his misfit classmate Kendra to an environmental rally at their school, she questions his motivations but reluctantly accepts. Later, Kyle blows Kendra off, prompting the spurned goth girl to cast a dark spell on the swaggering egotist.', '[{"name": "CBS Films", "id": 5490}, {"name": "Mel''s Cite du Cinema", "id": 54502}, {"name": "Storefront Films", "id": 60600}]', '2011-01-21', '43165571.00', '86.00', 'Love is never ugly.', 'Beastly', '6.0', 849, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzUzMTcxMTEzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTcwNjcxNA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2418, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'http://www.foxsearchlight.com/thehillshaveeyes/', 'en', 'Based on Wes Craven''s 1977 suspenseful cult classic, The Hills Have Eyes is the story of a family road trip that goes terrifyingly awry when the travelers become stranded in a government atomic zone. Miles from nowhere, the Carter family soon realizes the seemingly uninhabited wasteland is actually the breeding ground of a blood-thirsty mutant family...and they are the prey.', '[{"name": "Fox Searchlight Pictures", "id": 43}, {"name": "Dune Entertainment", "id": 444}, {"name": "Major Studio Partners", "id": 445}, {"name": "Craven-Maddalena Films", "id": 1600}]', '2006-03-10', '69623713.00', '107.00', 'The lucky ones die first.', 'The Hills Have Eyes', '6.1', 705, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzk0MTg5MzEyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDUyMzIzMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,7,190,281_.jpg'),
