(2432, '17000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://www.foxsearchlight.com/mylifeinruins/', 'en', 'A Greek tour guide named Georgia attempts to recapture her kefi (Greek for mojo) by guiding a ragtag group of tourists around Greece and showing them the beauty of her native land. Along the way, she manages to open their eyes to the wonders of an exotic foreign land while beginning to see the world through a new set of eyes in the process.', '[{"name": "Fox Searchlight Pictures", "id": 43}, {"name": "26 Films", "id": 2157}]', '2009-02-06', '20455276.00', '95.00', 'The most fun you can have without a passport.', 'My Life in Ruins', '5.6', 101, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTE3MzQ2NzczNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjgyNDgzMg@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2433, '17000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'The new season of "American Dreamz," the wildly popular television singing contest, has captured the country''s attention, as the competition looks to be between a young Midwestern gal (Moore) and a showtunes-loving young man from Orange County (Golzari). Recently awakened President Staton (Quaid) even wants in on the craze, as he signs up for the potential explosive season finale.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "Depth of Field", "id": 1473}]', '2006-03-04', '7314027.00', '107.00', 'Imagine a country where more people vote for a pop idol than they do for their next President.', 'American Dreamz', '4.9', 95, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjE0MTk1NzM4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTUzMjYzMQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg');
