(2493, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}, {"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Justice. Safe streets. Payback. Metallurgist John Henry Irons (O''Neal) vows to claim them all when a renegade military reject (Judd Nelson) puts new superweapons in dangerous hands. Helped by an electronics wiz (Annabeth Gish) and an imaginative scrap metal worker (Richard Roundtree), Irons becomes Steel. Wearing body armor, wielding a fearsome electrohammer and riding a gadget-packed motorcycle, he''s ready to wage war...if he can fix the untimely glitches in his untested gear. "You all be cool now," the good-guy hero tells two crime victims he rescues. There''ll be a lot of thrillin'' before Steel himself can start chillin.''', '[{"name": "Quincy Jones-David Salzman Entertainment", "id": 2554}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}, {"name": "DC Entertainment", "id": 9993}]', '1997-08-15', '1686429.00', '97.00', 'Heroes don''t come any bigger.', 'Steel', '4.3', 48, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGQ2ZTU0NjMtNjY0Ny00OGUxLWI5ZjItNzNmZDMzODhlMTY2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjUzOTY1NTc@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2494, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://theimmigrant-lefilm.com/', 'en', 'An innocent immigrant woman is tricked into a life of burlesque and vaudeville until a dazzling magician tries to save her and reunite her with her sister who is being held in the confines of Ellis Island.', '[{"name": "Kingsgate Films", "id": 770}, {"name": "Worldview Entertainment", "id": 9015}]', '2013-07-03', '5867686.00', '117.00', 'NA', 'The Immigrant', '6.2', 250, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjQ2OTAyNTUzNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTkxNzA2MTE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2495, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'The last movie from the team of Ismail Merchant, James Ivory, and Kazuo Ishiguro. Set in 1930s Shanghai, "The White Countess" is both Sofia (Natasha Richardson), a fallen member of the Russian aristocracy, and a nightclub created by a blind American diplomat named Jackson (Ralph Fiennes), who asks Sofia to be the centerpiece of the world he wants to create.', '[{"name": "Sony Pictures Classics", "id": 58}, {"name": "Shanghai Film Group", "id": 3407}, {"name": "Merchant Ivory Productions", "id": 20740}]', '2005-10-30', '0.00', '135.00', 'NA', 'The White Countess', '6.9', 21, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNWMwNzM1YjUtZjM4Ny00NDc1LTkwYmQtNGRkN2IyZjI5ZDE0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTcwOTQzOTYy._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2496, '20000000.00', '[{"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A fine art auctioneer mixed up with a gang, joins forces with a hypnotherapist to recover a lost painting. As boundaries between desire, reality and hypnotic suggestion begin to blur, the stakes rise faster than anyone could have anticipated.', '[{"name": "Cloud Eight Films", "id": 6708}, {"name": "Path\\u00e9", "id": 7981}, {"name": "Decibel Films", "id": 8286}, {"name": "Film4", "id": 9349}]', '2013-03-27', '24261569.00', '101.00', 'Don''t be a hero.', 'Trance', '6.5', 956, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjMzNjU1MTg5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTExMTcwOQ@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2497, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Following a ridiculously awful flight that leads to his pet''s death, Nashawn Wade files a lawsuit against the airline, and wins a multimillion-dollar settlement. Determined to create a better flying experience, Nashawn starts his own airline, one that caters to an African-American clientele. Going into business with a tricked-out plane piloted by the smooth Capt. Mack, the airline hits a snag when it has to deal with the family of Elvis Hunkee.', '[{"name": "Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer (MGM)", "id": 8411}]', '2004-05-28', '14822346.00', '86.00', 'Announcing the arrival of the first airline with soul.', 'Soul Plane', '4.7', 108, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc5NDcxNjg5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDIyNzczMw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2498, '11000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'http://www.bienvenuechezleschtis-lefilm.com/', 'fr', 'Although living a comfortable life in Salon-de-Provence, a charming town in the South of France, Julie has been feeling depressed for a while. To please her, Philippe Abrams, a post office administrator, her husband, tries to obtain a transfer to a seaside town, on the French Riviera, at any cost. The trouble is that he is caught red-handed while trying to scam an inspector. Philippe is immediately banished to the distant unheard of town of Bergues, in the Far North of France...', '[{"name": "Centre National de la Cin\\u00e9matographie", "id": 310}, {"name": "TF1 Films Productions", "id": 356}, {"name": "Path\\u00e9 Renn Productions", "id": 866}, {"name": "Hirsch", "id": 2355}, {"name": "Canal+", "id": 5358}, {"name": "Cin\\u00e9Cin\\u00e9ma", "id": 6301}, {"name": "R\\u00e9gion Nord-Pas-de-Calais", "id": 11434}, {"name": "Les Productions du Chicon", "id": 11544}, {"name": "Centre R\\u00e9gional des Ressources Audiovisuelles (CRRAV)", "id": 11545}]', '2008-01-09', '53191886.00', '106.00', 'NA', 'Welcome to the Sticks', '6.8', 615, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzJiYTU4MGMtYzlhNy00YWMxLTgyYWYtOTg1ZDMzMTgyZmNiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzQzNzQxNzI@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR11,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2499, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'The rise of national socialism in Germany should not be regarded as a conspiracy of madmen. Millions of "good" people found themselves in a society spiralling into terrible chaos. A film about then, which illuminates the terrors of now.', '[]', '2008-12-11', '0.00', '96.00', 'Anything that makes people happy can''t be bad can it?', 'Good', '6.3', 29, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjI5OTZhMjAtMTZkOC00NDM2LWFjMWMtMTcyZGMyY2Y2ZTc2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTM0NTU5Mg@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2500, '13000000.00', '[{"id": 14, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'http://www.ifcfilms.com/films/enter-the-void', 'en', 'This psychedelic tour of life after death is seen entirely from the point of view of Oscar (Nathaniel Brown), a young American drug dealer and addict living in Tokyo with his prostitute sister, Linda (Paz de la Huerta). When Oscar is killed by police during a bust gone bad, his spirit journeys from the past -- where he sees his parents before their deaths -- to the present -- where he witnesses his own autopsy -- and then to the future, where he looks out for his sister from beyond the grave.', '[{"name": "BIM Distribuzione", "id": 225}, {"name": "Wild Bunch", "id": 856}]', '2009-05-05', '754249.00', '161.00', 'NA', 'Enter the Void', '7.2', 387, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMGQwMWRmODEtYzYwMy00MzFiLWJhYWUtNWNkNWM0NWZhODBiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjQyMjcwNDM@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2501, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'The modern-day story focuses on two beautiful young vampires who are living the good nightlife in New York until love enters the picture and each has to make a choice that will jeopardize their immortality.', '[{"name": "Lucky Monkey Pictures", "id": 11093}, {"name": "Red Hour Films", "id": 12178}]', '2012-08-25', '0.00', '93.00', 'Dating Sucks', 'Vamps', '4.8', 91, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTg0ODkwMzI0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDc4OTc2OA@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR6,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2502, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A drama based on the true story of a college professor''s bond with the abandoned dog he takes into his home.', '[{"name": "Grand Army Entertainment", "id": 1843}, {"name": "Scion Films", "id": 7419}, {"name": "Inferno Distribution", "id": 11278}, {"name": "Stage 6 Films", "id": 11341}, {"name": "Hachiko", "id": 66327}, {"name": "Opperman Viner Chrystyn Entertainment", "id": 66328}]', '2009-06-13', '47801389.00', '93.00', 'A true story of faith, devotion and undying love.', 'Hachi: A Dog''s Tale', '7.7', 1717, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYmQzYjgyYzEtOTVhZC00MDRkLWJjNjItYzU3N2RiMTExZjA1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTcwOTQzOTYy._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,1,190,281_.jpg'),
(2503, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'As a child, Ali Neuman narrowly escaped being murdered by Inkhata, a militant political party at war with Nelson Mandela''s African National Congress. Only he and his mother survived the carnage of those years. But as with many survivors, the psychological scars remain.', '[{"name": "Eskwad", "id": 616}, {"name": "M6 Films", "id": 1115}, {"name": "Canal+", "id": 5358}, {"name": "Path\\u00e9", "id": 7981}, {"name": "Cin\\u00e9+", "id": 23616}, {"name": "Lobster Tree", "id": 34044}, {"name": "W9", "id": 34774}]', '2013-12-04', '0.00', '110.00', 'NA', 'Zulu', '6.7', 172, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjA0NjE1OTI0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDkyNTM3MDE@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR9,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2504, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 37, "name": "Western"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'When three women living on the edge of the American frontier are driven mad by harsh pioneer life, the task of saving them falls to the pious, independent-minded Mary Bee Cuddy. Transporting the women by covered wagon to Iowa, she soon realizes just how daunting the journey will be, and employs a low-life drifter, George Briggs, to join her. The unlikely pair and the three women head east, where a waiting minister and his wife have offered to take the women in. But the group first must traverse the harsh Nebraska Territories marked by stark beauty, psychological peril and constant threat.', '[{"name": "The Javelina Film Company", "id": 2322}, {"name": "EuropaCorp", "id": 6896}, {"name": "Ithaca Pictures", "id": 11765}]', '2014-05-18', '3442853.00', '122.00', 'NA', 'The Homesman', '6.4', 258, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQ4NTkxOTEyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTI1NzcwMzE@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
