(2506, '0.00', '[{"id": 10752, "name": "War"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A variety of characters, some close relatives, others distant strangers, are each affected by the making of a film about the Armenian Genocide of 1915.', '[{"name": "Alliance Atlantis Communications", "id": 803}, {"name": "Serendipity Point Films", "id": 805}, {"name": "Ego Film Arts", "id": 12800}]', '2002-05-20', '0.00', '115.00', 'NA', 'Ararat', '5.7', 16, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZThiZTZjN2EtMTllMC00ZjExLWFlNjQtNWM1YWMyM2MxMWEyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDkzNTM2ODg@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR2,0,190,281_.jpg'),
