(2534, '17000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'http://womaninblack.com/', 'en', 'The story follows a young lawyer, Arthur Kipps, who is ordered to travel to a remote village and sort out a recently deceased client’s papers. As he works alone in the client’s isolated house, Kipps begins to uncover tragic secrets, his unease growing when he glimpses a mysterious woman dressed only in black. Receiving only silence from the locals, Kipps is forced to uncover the true identity of the Woman in Black on his own, leading to a desperate race against time when he discovers her true identity.', '[{"name": "Hammer Film Productions", "id": 1314}, {"name": "UK Film Council", "id": 2452}, {"name": "Alliance Films", "id": 2514}, {"name": "Film i V\\u00e4st", "id": 6417}, {"name": "Talisman Productions", "id": 8989}, {"name": "Cross Creek Pictures", "id": 10246}, {"name": "Exclusive Media Group", "id": 11448}, {"name": "Filmgate Films", "id": 18230}]', '2012-02-01', '127730736.00', '95.00', 'What did they see?', 'The Woman in Black', '6.1', 1206, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjEwMzIxOTg3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjI4ODUzNw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2535, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/whenastrangercalls/site/', 'en', 'Far away from the site of a gruesome murder, a teenager named Jill Johnson arrives at a luxurious home for a baby-sitting job. With the children fast asleep, she settles in for what she expects to be an ordinary evening. Soon, the ringing of a phone and the frightening words of a sadistic caller turn Jill''s routine experience into a night of terror.', '[{"name": "Davis Entertainment", "id": 1302}, {"name": "Screen Gems", "id": 3287}]', '2006-02-03', '66966987.00', '87.00', 'Whatever You Do, Don''t Answer The Phone.', 'When a Stranger Calls', '5.4', 268, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTcyYjRhZTQtOTVlMy00MDU0LWFhNjktM2MyZDRmODgzMmNjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2536, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 10751, "name": "Family"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Fourteen-year-old Jason Shepherd (Muniz) has a reputation for stretching the truth. So, when big-time Hollywood producer Marty Wolf (Paul Giamatti) steals his class paper and turns it into a smash movie, no one believes Jason''s latest tall tale! On a cross-country adventure to set the record straight, Jason and best friend Kaylee (Bynes) devise a high-tech plan to squeeze the truth out of Wolf.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}]', '2002-02-08', '52970014.00', '88.00', 'The truth is never overrated', 'Big Fat Liar', '5.6', 197, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmEyNGFmODYtZjhjNC00NGViLTllMjQtYWYyZmQ1OGEzMzRlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2537, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10752, "name": "War"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A group of working-class friends decides to enlist in the Army during the Vietnam War and finds it to be hellish chaos -- not the noble venture they imagined. Before they left, Steven married his pregnant girlfriend -- and Michael and Nick were in love with the same woman. But all three are different men upon their return.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "EMI Films Ltd.", "id": 538}]', '1978-12-08', '50000000.00', '183.00', 'One of the most important and powerful films of all time!', 'The Deer Hunter', '7.8', 921, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDhmNTA0ZDMtYjhkNS00NzEzLWIzYTItOGNkMTVmYjE2YmI3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2538, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'During the final weeks of a presidential race, the President is accused of sexual misconduct. To distract the public until the election, the President''s adviser hires a Hollywood producer to help him stage a fake war.', '[{"name": "New Line Cinema", "id": 12}, {"name": "Tribeca Productions", "id": 11391}, {"name": "Baltimore Pictures", "id": 11407}]', '1997-12-25', '64256513.00', '97.00', 'A comedy about truth, justice and other special effects.', 'Wag the Dog', '6.7', 270, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzRkZDVkMDItYjk3Mi00NDkyLThmODUtYzhkN2EwZmE2ZTljXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,8,190,281_.jpg'),
