(2542, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 27, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 9648, "name": "Mystery"}, {"id": 878, "name": "Science Fiction"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'When some very creepy things start happening around school, the kids at Herrington High make a chilling discovery that confirms their worst suspicions: their teachers really are from another planet! As mind-controlling parasites rapidly begin spreading from the faculty to the students'' bodies, it''s ultimately up to the few who are left – an unlikely collection of loners, leaders, nerds and jocks – to save the world from alien domination.', '[{"name": "Dimension Films", "id": 7405}, {"name": "Los Hooligans Productions", "id": 11705}]', '1998-12-25', '40283321.00', '104.00', 'Take me to your teacher.', 'The Faculty', '6.2', 492, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTcwZGNiMWYtMTYwNC00MGVjLWI5OTQtODhkZTU4ZDZjOGNkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2543, '0.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10402, "name": "Music"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'A film about the singer Tina Turner and how she rose to stardom with her abusive husband Ike Turner and how she gained the courage to break free.', '[{"name": "Touchstone Pictures", "id": 9195}]', '1993-06-09', '0.00', '118.00', 'Who needs a heart when a heart can be broken?', 'What''s Love Got to Do with It', '6.9', 72, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYmQ1Yjk3N2UtODMwMy00MDVhLTkzNDctM2ZkODZmYzdhNjk3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjE5MjUyOTM@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(2544, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 28, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}]', 'http://www.miramax.com/movie/cop-land', 'en', 'Freddy Heflin is the sheriff of a place everyone calls “Cop Land” — a small and seemingly peaceful town populated by the big city police officers he’s long admired. Yet something ugly is taking place behind the town’s peaceful facade. And when Freddy uncovers a massive, deadly conspiracy among these local residents, he is forced to take action and make a dangerous choice between protecting his idols and upholding the law.', '[{"name": "Miramax Films", "id": 14}, {"name": "Across the River Productions", "id": 978}, {"name": "Woods Entertainment", "id": 979}]', '1997-08-15', '44862187.00', '104.00', 'No One Is Above The Law.', 'Cop Land', '6.6', 382, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmNhMzI0NmQtMzU1OS00NzQzLTg0NzctZDJkODZlMjU3OTc5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDc2NjEyMw@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(2545, '16000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'On a bet, a gridiron hero at John Hughes High School sets out to turn a bespectacled plain Jane into a beautiful and popular prom queen in this outrageous send-up of the teen movie genre.', '[{"name": "Original Film", "id": 333}, {"name": "Columbia Pictures Corporation", "id": 441}, {"name": "Neal H. Moritz Productions", "id": 2882}]', '2001-12-07', '66468332.00', '89.00', 'They served you Breakfast. They gave you Pie. Now we’re gonna stuff your face.', 'Not Another Teen Movie', '5.5', 431, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNGM1NDA5MDktMWFjZi00MmNkLWJmYTEtMTgwMWFmZTJjMzA4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUyOTc1NDYz._V1_QL75_UY281_CR1,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2546, '7000000.00', '[{"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Two young officers are marked for death after confiscating a small cache of money and firearms from the members of a notorious cartel during a routine traffic stop.', '[{"name": "Emmett/Furla Films", "id": 10405}, {"name": "Exclusive Media Group", "id": 11448}, {"name": "Hedge Fund Film Partners", "id": 11449}, {"name": "Crave Films", "id": 16312}, {"name": "Knightsbridge Entertainment", "id": 46961}, {"name": "Le Grisbi Productions", "id": 47169}, {"name": "5150 Action", "id": 47354}]', '2012-09-20', '48126384.00', '109.00', 'Every moment of your life they stand watch', 'End of Watch', '7.2', 1170, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjMxNjU0ODU5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjI4MzAyOA@@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,6,190,281_.jpg'),
(2547, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 53, "name": "Thriller"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Luke''s exultance at being selected for The Skulls (a secret society bred within the walls of a prominent Ivy League Campus) is soon overshadowed when he realises that all is ''not well in Wonderland''. For The Skulls is a breeding ground for the future powerful and elite. It''s not only a far cry from his working class background, but it also hallows its own deep and dark secrets.', '[{"name": "Universal Pictures", "id": 33}, {"name": "Original Film", "id": 333}, {"name": "Newmarket Capital Group", "id": 506}, {"name": "Cranium Films", "id": 11482}]', '2000-03-31', '35007180.00', '106.00', 'Getting in is easy. Getting out is a killer.', 'The Skulls', '5.8', 156, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODA2OTQ0NzctZTYwNi00N2E2LWJhN2UtOTc4N2UzYWRiOWVjL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,2,190,281_.jpg'),
(2548, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'http://www.focusfeatures.com/the_theory_of_everything', 'en', 'The Theory of Everything is the extraordinary story of one of the world’s greatest living minds, the renowned astrophysicist Stephen Hawking, who falls deeply in love with fellow Cambridge student Jane Wilde.', '[{"name": "Working Title Films", "id": 10163}]', '2014-11-26', '123726688.00', '123.00', 'His Mind Changed Our World. Her Love Changed His.', 'The Theory of Everything', '7.8', 3311, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTAwMTU4MDA3NDNeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDk4NTMxNTIx._V1_QL75_UX190_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2549, '0.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 80, "name": "Crime"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Bill Gluckman, a wealthy white Jewish senator is running for the office of Governor. His son "B-Rad" dresses, speaks, and acts as if he were a gangster from the inner city. The campaign team members hire two actors, who don''t know any more about inner-city life than B-Rad, to act as gang members, kidnap him, and take him to South Central Los Angeles where they hope Brad will be "scared white".', '[{"name": "Karz Entertainment", "id": 4194}, {"name": "Big Ticket Productions", "id": 4195}, {"name": "Warner Bros.", "id": 6194}]', '2003-04-10', '0.00', '86.00', 'NA', 'Malibu''s Most Wanted', '4.7', 77, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODM3NzE0NTMxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwMTIzNTk5._V1_QL75_UY281_CR0,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2550, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 35, "name": "Comedy"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 10749, "name": "Romance"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'Novalee Nation is a 17-year-old Tennessee transient who has to grow up in a hurry when she''s left pregnant and abandoned by her boyfriend on a roadside in Sequoyah, Okla., and takes refuge in the friendly aisles of Wal-Mart. In short order, some eccentric, kindly strangers "adopt" Novalee and her infant daughter, helping them buck the odds and build a new life.', '[{"name": "Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation", "id": 306}, {"name": "Wind Dancer Films", "id": 32803}]', '2000-04-27', '33771174.00', '120.00', 'Laughter is harder... Friendship is stronger... Trust is deeper... When it comes from the heart.', 'Where the Heart Is', '6.9', 155, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMGZkNjMxYWItYzRjZC00MzA2LWE0YWYtYjIzMmU2MTJiNmEyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTA0MjU0Ng@@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR10,0,190,281_.jpg'),
(2551, '15000000.00', '[{"id": 12, "name": "Adventure"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 36, "name": "History"}, {"id": 10752, "name": "War"}]', 'NA', 'en', 'An epic about British officer T.E. Lawrence''s mission to aid the Arab tribes in their revolt against the Ottoman Empire during the First World War. Lawrence becomes a flamboyant, messianic figure in the cause of Arab unity but his psychological instability threatens to undermine his achievements.', '[{"name": "Horizon Pictures (II)", "id": 11356}]', '1962-12-10', '69995385.00', '216.00', 'NA', 'Lawrence of Arabia', '7.8', 851, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWY5ZjhjNGYtZmI2Ny00ODM0LWFkNzgtZmI1YzA2N2MxMzA0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjUwNzk3NDc@._V1_QL75_UY281_CR3,0,190,281_.jpg'),
